1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dobrodošli u 55 minuta kod Željke Markić. Hvala da pratite moj YouTube kanal. Moja današnja gošća je misionarka Časna Dorotea Đunđer koja je već dugin iz godina djeluje u Beninu.

2
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Časna Dorotea, puno hvala da ste našli vremena na vašem godišnjem odmoru u Hrvatskoj za ovaj naš razgovor.

3
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam lijepo na pozivu i drago mi je da mogu par minuta podijeliti s vama.

4
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo se dvije upoznale u Beninu, dakle kad smo ga mi posjetili radi marijnih obroka. Vi ste se u stvari kroz to smo se upoznale. Vi ste otvorili dvije škole, sada već i tri škole.

5
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Četvrta se sad otvara u Beninu, je li tako?

6
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Peta, peta.

7
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, dakle mi smo preko veličatnog odilona koji je došao u Hrvatsku. Nekako se Hrvatska, na njegove župi su se upoznali sa njim, dakle želeći uz vratit mu su otvorili prvu kuhinju marijnih obroka Hrvati iz Varaždina, su otvorili u Beninu i onda smo kroz to upoznali i vas.

8
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Viste danas koordinirate sve kuhinje marijnih obroka u Beninu koje otvara u stvari marijni obroci Hrvatska.

9
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:46,799
[SPEAKER_01] Da, istina je. Prva kuhinja je otvorena preko veličasnog odilona, ali je bila jako vizana uz nas. Jer odilon je tu, jedini mi smo tamo koji bismo mogli to malo kao koordinirati.

10
00:01:47,000 --> 00:02:04,959
[SPEAKER_01] A s vremenom druga sela vidjeći kuhinju i dobro koje se čini toj djeci u tom selu, u tom školi, pa su tražili isto takvu kuhinje za njih. Danas ima puno tih sela, škola koje traže kuhinje.

11
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:26,060
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi moramo ići postepeno, polanko, tako kako bi mogli na neki način to dobro organizirati. Jer puno je djece, puno ih dolazi u školu, a mi smo tamo već dugo, dugo, puno prije nego što je odilon upoznao Hrvatsku, mi smo bili u Beninu.

12
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:35,719
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, mi smo bili u Beninu, a Hrvatska u stvari nije nas puno poznavala. Hrvatska je upoznala Benin preko veličasnog odilona.

13
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je na neki način, reći ćemo malo žalosno, ali dobro da je tako.

14
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:49,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ali dobro da je tako, pa na neki način i naš veličasni odilon je plod tog svog zajedničkog djelovanja u crkvi.

15
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] A sigurno.

16
00:02:50,300 --> 00:02:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako i tog misionarskog rada i ljubavi koja se ulaže već desetljećima u Benin. Vi ste u Benin došli prije...

17
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:04,060
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam došla u Benin 88. godine. Znači 33 godine sam ja u Beninu.

18
00:03:04,060 --> 00:03:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je bilo tako simpatično ono kako smo putovali zajedno i išli na sjever Benina kako ste...

19
00:03:11,300 --> 00:03:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vi u stvari govorite, kad govorite o Hrvatskoj, govorite mi Hrvatskoj.

20
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,560
[SPEAKER_00] Mi u Hrvatskoj.

21
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:18,379
[SPEAKER_00] A onda kad se govori o Beninu, govorite mi u Beninu.

22
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:26,560
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite, mi smo u Beninu i na neki način ja ću reći za sebe, ja sam srasla tamo u Beninu.

23
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,879
[SPEAKER_01] Kad me netko pita, sest, odakle ste došli iz Benina?

24
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:34,699
[SPEAKER_01] Uopće mi ne pada na pamet, da kažem, iz Zagreba ili iz Bosne.

25
00:03:34,699 --> 00:03:42,439
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam Hrvatica, rođena sam u Žepču, imam kuću, moje sestre imaju u Zagrebu u Beninu.

26
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] I jednom zgodom je da mi pozornio, sestra, kako je to rodit se u Beninu?

27
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] Tek mi je onda sinulo u svijest, u stvari što sam rekla.

28
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,819
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ja pa lijepo.

29
00:03:53,819 --> 00:03:57,740
[SPEAKER_01] Neki se negdje rađaju, neki se rađaju i dva puta.

30
00:03:58,400 --> 00:04:04,840
[SPEAKER_01] A to je u stvari moj slučaj i baš lijepo se rodit u Beninu i rasti s Beninom.

31
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kad ja pogledam sad unazad mojih tih 33 godine i onda vidim na neki način taj rast Benina i rast tog naroda.

32
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:20,600
[SPEAKER_01] Makar da smo još uvijek jako, jako daleko od Evrope.

33
00:04:21,259 --> 00:04:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] Što kopiramo od Evrope ono što je negativno za nas tamo u Beninu i što nas pritišće više i doleg zemlje.

34
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:33,259
[SPEAKER_01] A dobre stvari nekako idu teže.

35
00:04:33,259 --> 00:04:43,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sa tim marinim obrocima mi u Beninu, reći ću, činimo jako puno dobroga za taj narod.

36
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:49,060
[SPEAKER_01] Djeca dolaze u školu i škola završava u podne.

37
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] Od podne do 3 sata djeca imaju pauz.

38
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:57,339
[SPEAKER_01] U to vrijeme bi trebali otići kući, jest i vratit se.

39
00:04:57,339 --> 00:05:04,759
[SPEAKER_01] Mnoga djeca su daleko, a mnogi od njih nemaju ništa u podne za jest.

40
00:05:04,759 --> 00:05:09,660
[SPEAKER_01] Tek kad se roditelji vrate iz polja, onda će djeca jest, ali to je na većej.

41
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:17,519
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da mnoga djeca ostaju u školi, na putu, igraju se, ali bez obroka.

42
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:27,540
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon da je taj obrok koji naše djeca dobiju u podne je veliko bogatstvo za školu, za narod.

43
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se vidi u stvari velika promjena uspjeha djece koja imaju volju za učit, a nemaju mogućnosti.

44
00:05:36,699 --> 00:05:42,160
[SPEAKER_01] Svi mi znamo kako je teško nešto misliti ili raditi ako si gladan.

45
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:44,759
[SPEAKER_01] Sad djeca ujutro šta su jela? Ništa.

46
00:05:44,759 --> 00:05:56,180
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su došli u školu i neki su donijeli 50 franaka, 100 rijetki koji će nešto pojesti.

47
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:58,819
[SPEAKER_01] A 100 franaka vam nije ništa.

48
00:05:58,819 --> 00:06:02,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ti nemaš tu eto toliko da staviš dva zaloga je u usta.

49
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] Jer kod nas je danas postala hrana jako skupa.

50
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:10,279
[SPEAKER_01] I znači djeca su cijeli dan bez jela.

51
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:18,939
[SPEAKER_01] I onda što se događa sad kad mi otvorimo školu u jednom, kuhinju u jednoj školi.

52
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:27,139
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi raditelji iz susjednog sela premještaju svoju djecu u tu školu samo da bi imali taj obrok.

53
00:06:27,139 --> 00:06:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan u danu, tu kašu koja...

54
00:06:29,699 --> 00:06:36,939
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan u danu, to je nije baš kaša, to je jedan prilično zahvalan obrok za njih.

55
00:06:36,939 --> 00:06:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] Jer za naša djeca jako puno jedu.

56
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:42,240
[SPEAKER_01] Oni bi toga puno više pojeli da im se da.

57
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:50,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mi pratimo te mjere koje su nam određene, koje ne možemo ići u beskonać.

58
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:55,459
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo recite, evo vi imate tjedni, dakle meni, dakle od ponedeljka do petka.

59
00:06:55,459 --> 00:06:57,779
[SPEAKER_01] Što je ono što se djeci osigura?

60
00:06:57,779 --> 00:07:04,800
[SPEAKER_01] Tako programirano. Ja sam programirala tako da djeca jedu ponedeljkom rižu i dobiju jedno jaje.

61
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,459
[SPEAKER_01] Svako djete dobije jedno jaje.

62
00:07:06,459 --> 00:07:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] Utorkom djeca dobiju žgance, tu kukuruznu kašu sa nekakvim umakom od zelja i dobiju malo ribe.

63
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:18,319
[SPEAKER_01] To su istina malo ribe, ali to je za začin više.

64
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:21,759
[SPEAKER_01] Srijedom djeca dobiju grah.

65
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:30,939
[SPEAKER_01] Uz grah imaju ili grah je uz kukuruzno brašno ili jedan puta dajemo im uz to brašno od manjoke.

66
00:07:30,939 --> 00:07:35,060
[SPEAKER_01] Inače se to kod nas, to je naše glavno jelo i uvijek je to.

67
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:41,660
[SPEAKER_01] Onda četvrtkom ponovo imaju žgance uz umak od nekakvog zelja ili paradajza.

68
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:45,100
[SPEAKER_01] Onda petkom imaju ponovo rižu.

69
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:51,540
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste mi nekada, i kad smo bili djeca, neka djeca su po prvi puta pojela jaje.

70
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pa većina njih ne jedu oni jaje doma.

71
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,160
[SPEAKER_01] To je luksuz.

72
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:58,439
[SPEAKER_01] I ti nema ga.

73
00:07:58,439 --> 00:08:02,120
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, neće vam nijedno djete jesti da to ne jede doma.

74
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad vi pitate djecu, reći će jedemo.

75
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,279
[SPEAKER_01] Iako možda nisu nikad jeli.

76
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:10,920
[SPEAKER_01] Jer u njih je taj osjećaj.

77
00:08:11,699 --> 00:08:16,259
[SPEAKER_01] Ako on kaže da nema ili da ne jede, znači on sam sebe ponižava.

78
00:08:16,259 --> 00:08:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] A to oni ne želi.

79
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:21,180
[SPEAKER_01] I onda makro da je gladan, neće ti reći da je gladan.

80
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:26,259
[SPEAKER_00] Mene je ono baš oduševilo, više sam puta to vidjela u školama,

81
00:08:26,259 --> 00:08:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] kako neka djeca ostave dio hrane i nose kući u šalicama za svog mlađeg brata ili sestru koji ne ide u školu.

82
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on sam se nije najao, ali nosi kući za svog mlađeg brata.

83
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ima dosta djece koja ponesu od kuće nekakvu zdjelicu i onda tu hranu stave unutra, nešta će pojest.

84
00:08:47,539 --> 00:08:49,879
[SPEAKER_01] Ako idu u kući, onda će odnijet kuće.

85
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:53,240
[SPEAKER_01] Neki će ostati tu, pa će onda to poslije pojest.

86
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:59,440
[SPEAKER_01] Na kraju, jer od poodne do najveće šest sati je daleko.

87
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:03,720
[SPEAKER_01] I onda on, sad ću pojest malo, pa ću poslije dodati malo.

88
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,120
[SPEAKER_01] Ili pak nosi kući.

89
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da, vi ste, kako ste vi došli u Beninu?

90
00:09:08,059 --> 00:09:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ste vi došli u tu zemlju za koju kažete da vas raduje rast, da raste ona i da je vi uz nju isto ste raste?

91
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite, u tu zemlju smo otišle na sed dvije, sam 18. godina, ali to vam je jedan poziv nutarnji koji je teško objasniti i praktički nemoguće.

92
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:29,679
[SPEAKER_01] U nas pitaju zašto baš Benin? Ne znamo.

93
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:34,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to nam je Benin bio zasađen nekako u srce i samo tamo.

94
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo išli u Benin jednostavno da pomažemo tom narodu.

95
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,419
[SPEAKER_01] Oba dvije smo medicinske sestre.

96
00:09:41,419 --> 00:09:43,820
[SPEAKER_01] To mi je bio prvotni cilj.

97
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,919
[SPEAKER_01] Njihovo zdravstvena zaštita, ranca, djecom i to.

98
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:49,419
[SPEAKER_01] Istina, nismo mi puno znali.

99
00:09:49,419 --> 00:09:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ni potrebe Benina, ni mogućnosti.

100
00:09:52,539 --> 00:09:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vi ste kao časna redovnica u družbi se stara čudotvorne medaljice.

101
00:09:59,740 --> 00:10:02,700
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo željeli, osjetili se da bi željeli ići u misje?

102
00:10:02,700 --> 00:10:09,419
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio jedan poziv nutarnji koji praktički ja sam ga odbijala godinama, godinama i onda sam došla do kraja.

103
00:10:09,419 --> 00:10:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sad više, sad Norašić.

104
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,899
[SPEAKER_01] To vam je...

105
00:10:13,899 --> 00:10:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] Odbijali, odbijali.

106
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] Odbijali, na koncu si došao do zida.

107
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,399
[SPEAKER_01] Sad više ne možeš dalje.

108
00:10:19,399 --> 00:10:22,879
[SPEAKER_01] A mislim da je tako sa mnogim pozivima kud?

109
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ideš u nepoznatu.

110
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,419
[SPEAKER_01] U stvari ne znaš uopće kud ideš.

111
00:10:25,419 --> 00:10:26,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ni zašto ideš.

112
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali znaš da moraš ići.

113
00:10:28,539 --> 00:10:30,580
[SPEAKER_01] I tako smo nas dvije otišle.

114
00:10:30,580 --> 00:10:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] Poslali su nas.

115
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,779
[SPEAKER_01] Dobili smo jednu kuću.

116
00:10:33,779 --> 00:10:37,740
[SPEAKER_01] Biskupija nam je napravila kuću u jednom selu koji se zove Afame.

117
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:42,120
[SPEAKER_01] To je naša prvo selo i nama najdraže selo.

118
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,620
[SPEAKER_01] U tom selu nije bilo ništa.

119
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:48,200
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo imali ni vode, ni struje.

120
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,240
[SPEAKER_01] Došli smo u praznu kuću.

121
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,679
[SPEAKER_01] I onda poslije nešto nam je biskup dao.

122
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:54,240
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto smo mi privrijedili.

123
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:57,080
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi su iz sela nam donosili vodu.

124
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:59,240
[SPEAKER_01] Da ne idemo mi na rijeku.

125
00:11:00,279 --> 00:11:02,399
[SPEAKER_01] Voda je nije bila zdrava.

126
00:11:02,399 --> 00:11:04,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo kupovali prvo vrijeme vodu za pit.

127
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:07,320
[SPEAKER_01] Nas dvije pa toliko smo mogle.

128
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:12,279
[SPEAKER_01] I onda polako u selu praktički nije bilo ništa.

129
00:11:12,279 --> 00:11:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam bila jedina žena koja vozi.

130
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:17,740
[SPEAKER_01] I možda za neki desetak godina.

131
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] A osim toga na početku nije bilo možda 20 auta u cijelom Beninu.

132
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:26,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pa meni su rekli da kad ste vi tamo došli da ste vi bili jedina žena koja vozi u Beninu.

133
00:11:26,759 --> 00:11:28,759
[SPEAKER_00] U Beninu. Jedina žena u Beninu.

134
00:11:28,779 --> 00:11:33,320
[SPEAKER_01] U cijelom Beninu sam ja bila jedina žena koja vozi.

135
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:36,379
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle da ste vi bili prva bijelkinja koju su oni vidjeli.

136
00:11:36,379 --> 00:11:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je bijelaca.

137
00:11:37,539 --> 00:11:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] Bijeli se stara tamo.

138
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:41,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nitko od njih ne vozio.

139
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] Jer većina se stara niti danas ne vozio.

140
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,080
[SPEAKER_01] Oni imaju njihovog šofera.

141
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:48,779
[SPEAKER_01] A mi vozimo.

142
00:11:48,779 --> 00:11:52,779
[SPEAKER_01] Nemamo toliko srestava da bi plaćali šofera.

143
00:11:52,779 --> 00:11:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] I popravke auta za njim.

144
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,580
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ovako?

145
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] Mi kad vozimo znamo kud idemo.

146
00:11:58,779 --> 00:11:59,600
[SPEAKER_01] i kako vozimo.

147
00:11:59,600 --> 00:12:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vam moram reći.

148
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste tema naših razgovara i u obitelji.

149
00:12:03,139 --> 00:12:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kad smo bili prvi put u Beninu je bio moj suprok s nama.

150
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:07,779
[SPEAKER_00] I putovali smo gore visoko na sjever.

151
00:12:07,779 --> 00:12:08,940
[SPEAKER_00] I vi ste vozili.

152
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:10,379
[SPEAKER_00] Niste njemu dali da vozimo.

153
00:12:10,379 --> 00:12:11,600
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, ne, ne, ne.

154
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ga ubijem sada oko toga.

155
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sestra Dorotea ti nije dala mu voziti.

156
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ali rekao da ste odlična vozačica.

157
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:24,379
[SPEAKER_01] Čujte, neko strani vozi na nepoznatom putu.

158
00:12:24,379 --> 00:12:26,419
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad ne znaš.

159
00:12:26,419 --> 00:12:30,919
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam od prilike sve što bi se moglo na tom dogoditi.

160
00:12:31,179 --> 00:12:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, da, i to na putu vam je sve vidjeli ste.

161
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] I koze, i djeca, i ovce.

162
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:38,039
[SPEAKER_01] S tim je moraš računati.

163
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,120
[SPEAKER_01] A još kakav je put.

164
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vi ste, kako je to bilo kad ste vi došli iz Hrvatske,

165
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] tamo u tu kuću, u sred Afrike.

166
00:12:46,179 --> 00:12:47,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to bilo?

167
00:12:47,639 --> 00:12:49,240
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste tada koliko godina ste imali?

168
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sam tada imala 35 godina.

169
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:51,179
[SPEAKER_00] 35 godina.

170
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:55,700
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, najljepši vrijeme, najljepši život.

171
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:56,899
[SPEAKER_01] Bila sam u Zagrebu.

172
00:12:56,899 --> 00:12:58,259
[SPEAKER_01] Radila sam u bolnici.

173
00:12:58,259 --> 00:13:00,899
[SPEAKER_01] I to vreme mi je bilo baš najljepše.

174
00:13:00,899 --> 00:13:03,759
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš ograničeno svoje radno vrijeme.

175
00:13:03,759 --> 00:13:04,720
[SPEAKER_01] Završiš posao.

176
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ideš kući.

177
00:13:05,940 --> 00:13:08,259
[SPEAKER_01] Kod kuće imaš molitvu.

178
00:13:08,259 --> 00:13:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] I drugo, koliko stigneš pomoći drugima.

179
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:13,120
[SPEAKER_01] Ali eto, meni je rečeno, baš sad.

180
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] Izvoli, Doroteja, trebam te u Beninu.

181
00:13:15,679 --> 00:13:16,480
[SPEAKER_01] Baš sad.

182
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:19,580
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo došli tamo u sve to.

183
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:21,100
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne znam.

184
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,440
[SPEAKER_01] To je, mislim, posebna Božja milost.

185
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da mi nismo osjetili tu prazninu, niti nekakav nedostatak.

186
00:13:28,059 --> 00:13:34,539
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su nam drugi pričali, kako su oni iz početka imali averziju prema tome.

187
00:13:34,539 --> 00:13:37,840
[SPEAKER_01] Jedino, bilo mi je ono, strašno, sve je bilo prljavo.

188
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,059
[SPEAKER_00] Prljavo, da, da.

189
00:13:39,059 --> 00:13:40,600
[SPEAKER_01] Sve je bilo prljavo.

190
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:43,639
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi nisu imali naviku čišćenja.

191
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:45,580
[SPEAKER_01] Danas čistim, sutra će opet biti prljavo.

192
00:13:45,580 --> 00:13:51,100
[SPEAKER_01] I praktički, ređeću, mi smo počeli sa tim čišćenjem, uređivanjem.

193
00:13:52,019 --> 00:13:54,379
[SPEAKER_01] I ono me smetalo, to mi je išlo po glavi.

194
00:13:54,379 --> 00:13:56,639
[SPEAKER_01] Svi koji su hodali, vukli su noge.

195
00:13:56,639 --> 00:13:59,580
[SPEAKER_01] Čuješ i na deset metara.

196
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,740
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pa ne možete dignuti noge, po tako.

197
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:05,820
[SPEAKER_01] Danas toga više već nema.

198
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:10,620
[SPEAKER_01] Te dvije stvari i danas svi gledaju da to bude čisto.

199
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:12,419
[SPEAKER_01] Oni će pomesti ispred svoje kuće.

200
00:14:12,419 --> 00:14:16,039
[SPEAKER_00] Da, vidi ih se često ujutro, baš kako čiste ispred kuće.

201
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:17,899
[SPEAKER_01] Da, no, oni čiste ispred kuće.

202
00:14:17,899 --> 00:14:20,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je posignuto na taj način.

203
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:24,600
[SPEAKER_01] Oni imaju, svi vjeruju u te, koje kakve vračke.

204
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:30,220
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, to su nama, kad smo mi došli, onda su nas učili kako se tamo trebamo ponašat.

205
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:35,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ujutro prije nego izađeš iz kuće, ti moraš, izlaziš sa metlom i meteš ispred sebe.

206
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:38,899
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti je netko bacio nekakvu...

207
00:14:38,899 --> 00:14:41,700
[SPEAKER_00] A kao čini, kao nekakve čarolije, da, da, da.

208
00:14:41,700 --> 00:14:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ćeš ti to metlom očistiti.

209
00:14:43,860 --> 00:14:46,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ja, ja to nikad neću rati.

210
00:14:46,519 --> 00:14:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, to se mora. Ja ne.

211
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:52,120
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mene, dragi Bog, neće zaštiti to, to ga, neće ni metla.

212
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja u to vjerujem.

213
00:14:53,960 --> 00:15:00,399
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, ali to je kod njih, to su izmislili stari, da bi mlade prisilili da,

214
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:03,100
[SPEAKER_01] metu, da bude čisto oko kuće.

215
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:04,799
[SPEAKER_01] Nema tu ništa.

216
00:15:04,799 --> 00:15:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] Metla ni može ništa učiniti.

217
00:15:06,759 --> 00:15:11,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, evo, tu su ta vjerovanja, ali svako to vjerovanje ima svoj razlog zašto.

218
00:15:11,399 --> 00:15:13,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je nekog većih dobra.

219
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:19,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, dakle, vi ste, voda nije bila dobra, higijena, nikakvi uvjeti, ono, u toj kući.

220
00:15:19,139 --> 00:15:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste sami malariju nekoliko puta dobili.

221
00:15:21,460 --> 00:15:23,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, malariju, ne znam, nije, sto puta.

222
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,899
[SPEAKER_01] Na početku su bile to teške malarije.

223
00:15:25,899 --> 00:15:30,399
[SPEAKER_01] I, ono, temperaturu imaš bolove.

224
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:34,419
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad budeš, imaš povraćanje, proljevi.

225
00:15:34,419 --> 00:15:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ne možeš glavu dignuti.

226
00:15:36,299 --> 00:15:43,580
[SPEAKER_01] Jest, već, da si dalekati, netko nosi hranu, osjetiš mirist, ma kakvi ni blizu.

227
00:15:43,580 --> 00:15:45,700
[SPEAKER_01] Onda, malo, pomalo.

228
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] Na početku mi smo, ono, istini za volju, malo smo, premalo smo pazili na sebe.

229
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:53,440
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo se dali na rad za taj narod.

230
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:55,379
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da im pomognete što više.

231
00:15:55,379 --> 00:16:00,580
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i onda smo mi na neki način, reći ću, malo te ne zaboravili, redovito jest.

232
00:16:00,580 --> 00:16:02,740
[SPEAKER_01] Na brzinu nešto pojedeš.

233
00:16:02,740 --> 00:16:09,700
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su nas upozoravali, ti sveđenici, sestre, vi morate jest, vi morate misliti na sebe, vi ne možete non stop raditi.

234
00:16:10,299 --> 00:16:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] I onda, ja sam znala biti, imam malariju i sad došli su u ambulantu.

235
00:16:14,659 --> 00:16:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] Dovode djecu, dolaze teško bolesni, da.

236
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] Donose sa djecom.

237
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:27,279
[SPEAKER_01] Onda oni meni nekad donesu mi djete u krevet, da ja vidim, da onda potvrdim sestri što će s njim, kako će s njim.

238
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:29,659
[SPEAKER_01] A nekad se digne pa dođem tamo sjednem.

239
00:16:29,659 --> 00:16:30,879
[SPEAKER_01] Ma, sva šta smo imali.

240
00:16:31,580 --> 00:16:35,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan put su nam, ja sam imala baš malariju, donijeli su nam, doveli su nam jednog.

241
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:38,620
[SPEAKER_01] Kako su se djeca igrala i njemu su osjekli prst.

242
00:16:38,620 --> 00:16:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, prst je tu, malo se drži na koži.

243
00:16:42,940 --> 00:16:46,200
[SPEAKER_01] I ma kaže, ne bude da idu u bolnicu, to bi trebalo skinuti.

244
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, oni ne mogu ići u bolnicu, sestrovi napravi tešto.

245
00:16:49,539 --> 00:16:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bojim se da će to biti još gore.

246
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,259
[SPEAKER_01] Inficirat će se.

247
00:16:55,259 --> 00:16:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se ne držim na nogama, ja sjedim.

248
00:16:58,159 --> 00:17:00,419
[SPEAKER_01] Bolesni, teško vida.

249
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] Malo sam to očistila i onako, ja kažem, ja ću to zamotati, a morate mi doći svaki dan.

250
00:17:06,140 --> 00:17:11,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja vidim, ako no kad poplavi, morate ići u bolnicu.

251
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se to mora skinuti, jer će otići cijela ruka.

252
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] Volje skinuti jedan prst, nego cijelu ruku.

253
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:20,579
[SPEAKER_01] Samo vi to napravite, oni su sigurni da će to biti dobro.

254
00:17:20,579 --> 00:17:24,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam to tako zbilja i napravila, stavila kost, je bila presjećena.

255
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:28,259
[SPEAKER_01] A ja sam stavila kost na kost, malo je bio okrenut nasranu.

256
00:17:28,259 --> 00:17:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] I to se začudo primilo.

257
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:34,759
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nevjerojatno.

258
00:17:34,759 --> 00:17:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ja poslije razmišljam, da je to neko, da je to bilo u bolnici.

259
00:17:38,519 --> 00:17:41,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ima ništa drugo nego osjeći, samo malo koza se drži.

260
00:17:42,019 --> 00:17:48,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to se primilo, su meni došli i rekli, evo sestra, joj on može micat prstom sve, samo je malo vidi se da je okrenut.

261
00:17:48,339 --> 00:17:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

262
00:17:48,779 --> 00:17:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] Bez šta, dobro.

263
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, bilo je tako teško.

264
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:57,799
[SPEAKER_01] Ali eto, hvala Bogu, mi smo uz sve te nevolje.

265
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] To je sve prošlo.

266
00:17:59,420 --> 00:18:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, kad ti dođete malarija, kad ti stisne se, onda se pitaš, ma kud sam došla, jel mi to trebalo?

267
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] I misliš, čim to prođe od veja kući?

268
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:09,759
[SPEAKER_00] A kad prođe, ono, opet zaboraviš.

269
00:18:09,759 --> 00:18:12,799
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa da, čovjek, jasno mi je to.

270
00:18:12,799 --> 00:18:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] To je vaš, sada je to...

271
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je zvanje, to je poziv.

272
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] I ti ne možeš biti sretan ako nisi tu gdje te Bog hoće.

273
00:18:21,019 --> 00:18:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš ti sve drugo imati, ali ako nisi tu gdje te Bog hoće, nićeš biti sretan do kraja.

274
00:18:26,039 --> 00:18:33,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sad je doista impresivno kako ste u ovih 30 godina kuća koja je u AFAME, u ambulanta.

275
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] kuća koja je, dakle, imate tri kuće ili imate četiri sirotište za djeto.

276
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:41,220
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, toliko od toga ste uvih 30.

277
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ono što je najvažnije, imate pune kuće sestara mladih sa zvanjima.

278
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mi imamo trenutno 36 domaćih sestara.

279
00:18:51,539 --> 00:18:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, recimo, nas smo tri, ali imamo šest zajednica.

280
00:19:00,259 --> 00:19:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] Sestre rade, imamo dvije ambulante naše gdje mi radimo.

281
00:19:04,779 --> 00:19:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] Onda i sestre rade u bolnici, jedna radi u laboratoriju, dvije rade u školi.

282
00:19:10,539 --> 00:19:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] Onda imamo ta dva sirotišta gdje smo, mi koji smo tu radimo sve druge posle, onda još i tu.

283
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:24,779
[SPEAKER_01] Da sad trebamo otvoriti jednu novu ambulantu, ne našu, nego u nekom selu.

284
00:19:24,779 --> 00:19:30,799
[SPEAKER_01] Sel nam je dosta daleko, ali su nas molili da tamo dođemo raditi djece.

285
00:19:30,799 --> 00:19:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bila jedna ambulanta koja je isključivo za djecu.

286
00:19:34,779 --> 00:19:38,759
[SPEAKER_01] Sad mi trebamo urediti, opremiti tu ambulantu.

287
00:19:38,759 --> 00:19:41,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, sestre imamo koje bi radile tu.

288
00:19:41,619 --> 00:19:44,259
[SPEAKER_01] Sad treba dati sve što treba.

289
00:19:44,259 --> 00:19:49,339
[SPEAKER_00] Opremiti ambulantu i sa svim priborom koji je potreban, sa opremom.

290
00:19:49,339 --> 00:19:51,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što treba je, zad vam je to, ne možete vi.

291
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:57,359
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo mi došli tamo, onda smo, no i biskup je mogla lako otvoriti jednu ambulantu, sve to išlo.

292
00:19:57,740 --> 00:20:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] Ali danas toga više nema, jer država mi je postavila takav zakon i one zahtjevaju to i to, ali vam ništa ne daju.

293
00:20:05,180 --> 00:20:10,440
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa to je ono što smo pričali o koroni, kako se sad kao protiv korone bori.

294
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:18,319
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan u Beninu i danas umire najmanje 15 do 20 osoba od malarije.

295
00:20:18,319 --> 00:20:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan u Beninu cijelo.

296
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:22,660
[SPEAKER_01] Nitko se ne postavlja nikakvo pitanje.

297
00:20:22,660 --> 00:20:25,299
[SPEAKER_01] Izlječiva, bolest, može ju se vijeti.

298
00:20:25,299 --> 00:20:29,900
[SPEAKER_01] A sad nekakva korona koju smo izmislili, otkud?

299
00:20:29,900 --> 00:20:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] I sad imaju zaštite, ugraničenja, ne smiješ, ne smiješ.

300
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:43,220
[SPEAKER_01] Nas su tamo maltrtirali više mjesec dana, nismo, dva mjeseca, nismo mogli izaći 500 metara iz kuće prema gradu.

301
00:20:43,220 --> 00:20:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] Korona.

302
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,460
[SPEAKER_00] Puna kuća, djece, siročadi.

303
00:20:46,460 --> 00:20:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ako vas je, da, 50 u kući.

304
00:20:49,099 --> 00:20:50,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ja jedan dan se napravila.

305
00:20:50,980 --> 00:20:55,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa idem, nema više kruha, nema više, nema hrane za životinje.

306
00:20:55,019 --> 00:20:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, sreća, imali smo kukuru, zrižu i to, nema za životinje.

307
00:20:58,539 --> 00:21:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa idem, pa idem si kupit hrane, no.

308
00:21:01,579 --> 00:21:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ne može, kaže mi, znate šta, meni je sve jedno, umrijet od korone ili umrijet od gladi.

309
00:21:07,579 --> 00:21:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] Više volim umrijet od korone.

310
00:21:09,859 --> 00:21:11,680
[SPEAKER_01] To ide brže, ako treba.

311
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:14,299
[SPEAKER_01] A nas je 50 u kući, ja imam djecu.

312
00:21:14,299 --> 00:21:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] Djeca ne znaju za koronu, djeca će i jest.

313
00:21:17,180 --> 00:21:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

314
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:20,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje, reko jedan policaj, sma, pustite ju, nek ide.

315
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:23,160
[SPEAKER_01] I tako sam prošla u grad, kupila hranu i za nas.

316
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, to izbijam, pa smiješno zvuči.

317
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kad slušam, ono, u medijima te priče o mjerama u afričkim zemljama protiv korone,

318
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:33,579
[SPEAKER_00] to je doista, izgleda kao ruganje.

319
00:21:33,579 --> 00:21:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] Kada znateš da djeca od gladi umiru, od bolesti koje su izlječive,

320
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] od proljeva, od stotinu drugih bolesti,

321
00:21:42,900 --> 00:21:47,240
[SPEAKER_00] od kojih ne bi se opće trebalo umirat danas u 21. stoljeću,

322
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:50,299
[SPEAKER_00] a onda ti pričaju da se dezinficiraju ruke u selima

323
00:21:50,299 --> 00:21:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] kojima nema opće vode, niti kanalizacije, niti ičega, mislimo.

324
00:21:53,519 --> 00:21:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da, tko je to...

325
00:21:55,519 --> 00:21:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] A to je...

326
00:21:56,819 --> 00:21:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] Cijeli van na van jedna izmišljena priča.

327
00:21:59,559 --> 00:22:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] Oda smo još, ono, u komunizmu, samo priča bezvezna.

328
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:06,180
[SPEAKER_01] Čujte, tako se radi u Evropi, tako mi moramo raditi.

329
00:22:06,180 --> 00:22:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

330
00:22:06,599 --> 00:22:08,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kopirati, kopirati bez obzira...

331
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,740
[SPEAKER_01] Kopija se neke stvari.

332
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] Što se sve, ništa drugo ne može usporediti.

333
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naše ljudi kažu, tako se radi u Evropi,

334
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:18,480
[SPEAKER_01] pa dajte nam onda evropske plaće i evropsku hranu.

335
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

336
00:22:19,059 --> 00:22:20,400
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćemo se onda držati toga.

337
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:20,660
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

338
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:26,880
[SPEAKER_01] One, mi se borimo, idemo tamo u polje, suša, dve godine, nema kiše, normalno.

339
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:30,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi stiju kukuruz i na koncu ništa ne uberu.

340
00:22:30,579 --> 00:22:33,240
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je ti da plaćeš.

341
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:33,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da.

342
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] Naša je guća tu, mi smo nešto malo posijali kod nas.

343
00:22:36,299 --> 00:22:38,859
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko smo posijali, ipak smo nešto ubrali.

344
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] A ljudi nasuprot nas su posijali hektare.

345
00:22:41,539 --> 00:22:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] Niti jedno klipa nisu ubrali.

346
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ove godine je ista stvar.

347
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,339
[SPEAKER_01] Prva sezona je već propala.

348
00:22:48,339 --> 00:22:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] Prije onak sam ja došla iz Afrike,

349
00:22:50,119 --> 00:22:52,220
[SPEAKER_01] vidjela sam da je njihova sezona propala.

350
00:22:52,220 --> 00:22:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam dva puta sjela kukuruz.

351
00:22:54,460 --> 00:22:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi puta ništa nije niklo,

352
00:22:56,619 --> 00:22:58,259
[SPEAKER_01] drugi puta je niklo vrlo malo

353
00:22:58,259 --> 00:22:59,440
[SPEAKER_01] i to su tanke.

354
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ti, od toga ništa ne može biti.

355
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:04,980
[SPEAKER_01] Sam ja rekla sestrama, idemo posaditi manjoku.

356
00:23:04,980 --> 00:23:06,680
[SPEAKER_01] Možda nešto bude.

357
00:23:07,519 --> 00:23:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Manjoka je, dakle, recite nam što je to manjoka.

358
00:23:10,519 --> 00:23:12,339
[SPEAKER_01] Manjoka je to vam jedna biljka

359
00:23:12,339 --> 00:23:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] koja ima korijen dole.

360
00:23:13,579 --> 00:23:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] To su korijeni, znaju biti dugački, veliki.

361
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,839
[SPEAKER_01] Ovisi o kvaliteti zemlje.

362
00:23:16,839 --> 00:23:19,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je plodnija zemlja,

363
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:20,740
[SPEAKER_01] onda ćete dobiti veće korijene,

364
00:23:20,740 --> 00:23:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] imate više.

365
00:23:21,539 --> 00:23:24,160
[SPEAKER_01] Onda manjoka mora biti u zemlji

366
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] od kad ju posadite do,

367
00:23:26,079 --> 00:23:28,220
[SPEAKER_01] kad ju vadite od prilike devet mjeseci,

368
00:23:28,220 --> 00:23:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] devet do deset mjeseci.

369
00:23:29,599 --> 00:23:31,740
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je zrela, ju berete,

370
00:23:31,740 --> 00:23:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] čupate u stvari,

371
00:23:33,539 --> 00:23:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] mora se oguli se,

372
00:23:35,420 --> 00:23:37,059
[SPEAKER_01] melje se, cijedi se,

373
00:23:37,180 --> 00:23:38,839
[SPEAKER_01] da se taj škrob odvoji.

374
00:23:38,839 --> 00:23:40,220
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ti sam vidjela da kako radite.

375
00:23:40,220 --> 00:23:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da, mi to radimo,

376
00:23:41,119 --> 00:23:42,940
[SPEAKER_01] mi uzimamo škrob za druge stvari,

377
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] onda ćemo i to preraditi.

378
00:23:44,279 --> 00:23:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] A onda to brašno,

379
00:23:45,579 --> 00:23:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] to što ostaje,

380
00:23:46,619 --> 00:23:47,740
[SPEAKER_01] to se prži.

381
00:23:48,940 --> 00:23:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] i mi to spremamo na naš način,

382
00:23:51,980 --> 00:23:53,140
[SPEAKER_01] da se dobro upržiti,

383
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] pomože i godinu i više,

384
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:57,700
[SPEAKER_01] biti onako ako je dobro zatvoreno,

385
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] stavljaju se u najlonske vreće,

386
00:23:59,460 --> 00:24:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa u druge,

387
00:24:00,119 --> 00:24:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] tako da zrak ne ulazi.

388
00:24:01,519 --> 00:24:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] E kad dođe zrak,

389
00:24:02,920 --> 00:24:04,279
[SPEAKER_01] onda on gubi svoj miris

390
00:24:04,279 --> 00:24:07,160
[SPEAKER_01] i gubi kvalitetu,

391
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:07,880
[SPEAKER_01] povlaži,

392
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,660
[SPEAKER_01] onda nije to.

393
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] a onda ovaj škrob što ostane,

394
00:24:10,599 --> 00:24:11,720
[SPEAKER_01] onda to opet pržimo

395
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,279
[SPEAKER_01] i opet spremamo na drugi način,

396
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:14,259
[SPEAKER_01] to nam je sve zajelo.

397
00:24:14,259 --> 00:24:15,599
[SPEAKER_00] Vi u principu,

398
00:24:15,599 --> 00:24:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] sada u svojim,

399
00:24:17,359 --> 00:24:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] vi uzgajate,

400
00:24:18,319 --> 00:24:19,519
[SPEAKER_00] imate životinje,

401
00:24:19,519 --> 00:24:21,660
[SPEAKER_00] sadite voće,

402
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] povrće.

403
00:24:22,519 --> 00:24:23,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u principu,

404
00:24:23,740 --> 00:24:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] samo održivo funkcionirate,

405
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] vaše zajednice,

406
00:24:27,460 --> 00:24:29,779
[SPEAKER_00] ili vi onda kao grupa funkcionirate,

407
00:24:29,779 --> 00:24:31,339
[SPEAKER_00] de facto samo održivo,

408
00:24:31,339 --> 00:24:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se možete za sve što možete

409
00:24:33,000 --> 00:24:35,200
[SPEAKER_00] sami svojim radom pobrinuti.

410
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] Istina,

411
00:24:35,599 --> 00:24:37,160
[SPEAKER_01] od samog početka,

412
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,160
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo mi došli tamo,

413
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:38,740
[SPEAKER_01] ili smo dvije,

414
00:24:38,740 --> 00:24:39,839
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo malo povrće,

415
00:24:39,839 --> 00:24:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] onda povremeno,

416
00:24:40,539 --> 00:24:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] sve smo više radili meso,

417
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:44,059
[SPEAKER_01] već najmanje deset godina

418
00:24:44,059 --> 00:24:45,019
[SPEAKER_01] nikad ne kupujemo.

419
00:24:45,019 --> 00:24:46,599
[SPEAKER_01] Zelje,

420
00:24:46,599 --> 00:24:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] to povrće nismo nikad kupovali.

421
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:51,819
[SPEAKER_01] I onda si brašno od manjoke,

422
00:24:51,819 --> 00:24:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] to sami isto napravimo.

423
00:24:53,119 --> 00:24:54,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nemamo svoju manjoku,

424
00:24:54,299 --> 00:24:55,200
[SPEAKER_01] kupimo korijen.

425
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:57,700
[SPEAKER_01] I onda si pravimo to brašno,

426
00:24:57,700 --> 00:24:59,339
[SPEAKER_01] ulje od palmi,

427
00:24:59,339 --> 00:25:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] crveno ulje,

428
00:25:00,059 --> 00:25:01,160
[SPEAKER_01] isto sami pravimo.

429
00:25:01,160 --> 00:25:03,220
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo nešto od svojih palmi,

430
00:25:03,220 --> 00:25:04,480
[SPEAKER_01] ali kupimo

431
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:06,779
[SPEAKER_01] taj

432
00:25:06,779 --> 00:25:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako se to kaže,

433
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,440
[SPEAKER_01] ni ne znam reći na hrvatske,

434
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] te plodove,

435
00:25:11,119 --> 00:25:11,779
[SPEAKER_01] palmine.

436
00:25:11,779 --> 00:25:14,160
[SPEAKER_01] I onda od toga mi pravimo ulje.

437
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko nama treba

438
00:25:15,420 --> 00:25:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] za naše zajednice,

439
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:17,839
[SPEAKER_01] za našu djecu,

440
00:25:17,839 --> 00:25:18,720
[SPEAKER_01] koja su s nama,

441
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,200
[SPEAKER_01] to isto ne kupujemo.

442
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] I onda

443
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:23,220
[SPEAKER_01] kupujemo sol,

444
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:23,740
[SPEAKER_01] šećer,

445
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:24,279
[SPEAKER_01] rižu,

446
00:25:24,279 --> 00:25:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] te stvari što sami

447
00:25:25,319 --> 00:25:26,440
[SPEAKER_01] ne možemo proizvesti.

448
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,240
[SPEAKER_00] ali ono što sam i vidjela

449
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:28,799
[SPEAKER_00] je da u stvari

450
00:25:28,799 --> 00:25:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] vi cijelim tim svojim životom,

451
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] s jedne strane,

452
00:25:33,839 --> 00:25:36,819
[SPEAKER_00] ekonomijom koju vodite,

453
00:25:36,819 --> 00:25:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari podučavate

454
00:25:38,059 --> 00:25:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] cijelo vrijeme ljude,

455
00:25:39,420 --> 00:25:41,660
[SPEAKER_00] kako da oni sebe organiziraju,

456
00:25:41,660 --> 00:25:44,180
[SPEAKER_00] kako da oni žive što bolje.

457
00:25:44,299 --> 00:25:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite,

458
00:25:44,579 --> 00:25:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] mi imamo djecu.

459
00:25:45,519 --> 00:25:47,259
[SPEAKER_01] I djeca idu u školu,

460
00:25:47,259 --> 00:25:48,779
[SPEAKER_01] sva dnaša djeca idu u školu.

461
00:25:48,779 --> 00:25:50,880
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo dvije kuće djecu.

462
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:52,359
[SPEAKER_01] To je od 90,

463
00:25:52,359 --> 00:25:54,259
[SPEAKER_01] između 90 do 100 djece.

464
00:25:54,259 --> 00:25:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] To su djeca...

465
00:25:55,619 --> 00:25:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] Curice,

466
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] to su curice,

467
00:25:57,180 --> 00:25:57,740
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

468
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] najmanja sad kod mene

469
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,339
[SPEAKER_01] ima pet godina,

470
00:26:00,339 --> 00:26:01,059
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam ju uzela

471
00:26:01,059 --> 00:26:02,019
[SPEAKER_01] sa godinu dana.

472
00:26:02,019 --> 00:26:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] Bez majke je,

473
00:26:03,579 --> 00:26:05,160
[SPEAKER_01] otac joj je praktički ostavio.

474
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] I to su djeca koja

475
00:26:06,759 --> 00:26:09,579
[SPEAKER_01] su bez jednog i bez oba roditelja,

476
00:26:09,579 --> 00:26:11,400
[SPEAKER_01] koji nam je netko molio

477
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:12,180
[SPEAKER_01] da ih primimo.

478
00:26:12,180 --> 00:26:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] kojem nisu obi nije mogla preuzeta.

479
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

480
00:26:15,119 --> 00:26:17,539
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mi radimo uglavnom,

481
00:26:17,539 --> 00:26:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] ali ta djeca moraju raditi uz nas.

482
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da su oni svi nauče

483
00:26:22,400 --> 00:26:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] kako danas sutra,

484
00:26:24,519 --> 00:26:28,440
[SPEAKER_01] kad postanu odrasle osobe,

485
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:30,359
[SPEAKER_01] imaju svoj kruh na neki način,

486
00:26:30,359 --> 00:26:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] onda će uvijek moći nešto pored.

487
00:26:32,539 --> 00:26:34,740
[SPEAKER_01] Malo zelja,

488
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:36,299
[SPEAKER_01] to zelje koje mi koristimo,

489
00:26:36,299 --> 00:26:38,319
[SPEAKER_01] to je skupo na drežnici,

490
00:26:38,319 --> 00:26:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali onako pored,

491
00:26:39,519 --> 00:26:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] kad sebi posadiš

492
00:26:40,599 --> 00:26:41,579
[SPEAKER_01] srednu obitelj,

493
00:26:41,859 --> 00:26:42,859
[SPEAKER_01] dva, tri struka,

494
00:26:42,859 --> 00:26:43,859
[SPEAKER_01] ta ljuta paprika,

495
00:26:43,859 --> 00:26:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] koju oni jako puno jedu.

496
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,759
[SPEAKER_01] Kad se tu posadi

497
00:26:46,759 --> 00:26:47,519
[SPEAKER_01] za jednu obitelj,

498
00:26:47,519 --> 00:26:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] tri struka,

499
00:26:48,519 --> 00:26:49,900
[SPEAKER_01] sasvim dovoljno.

500
00:26:49,900 --> 00:26:51,839
[SPEAKER_01] I na taj način

501
00:26:51,839 --> 00:26:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] oni se uče.

502
00:26:52,619 --> 00:26:55,640
[SPEAKER_01] Od nas je otišla jedna djevojka

503
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] za, recimo,

504
00:26:57,460 --> 00:26:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] na jednu farmu,

505
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] da se malo nauči

506
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,559
[SPEAKER_01] o poljoprivredi.

507
00:27:02,660 --> 00:27:03,680
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ona je tamo bila

508
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] na nekakvoj praksi,

509
00:27:05,420 --> 00:27:06,599
[SPEAKER_01] škola, recimo,

510
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:08,319
[SPEAKER_01] godinu i pol,

511
00:27:08,319 --> 00:27:10,180
[SPEAKER_01] do dvije godine budu

512
00:27:10,180 --> 00:27:11,640
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ja sam išla

513
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] u posjetu,

514
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,460
[SPEAKER_01] jer ono što treba,

515
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] što nema tamo,

516
00:27:15,319 --> 00:27:15,599
[SPEAKER_01] uglavno,

517
00:27:15,599 --> 00:27:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] mi financiramo.

518
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:20,319
[SPEAKER_01] za meni je lako,

519
00:27:20,319 --> 00:27:21,359
[SPEAKER_01] jer ja to sve znam.

520
00:27:21,359 --> 00:27:22,339
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ona je sve naučila

521
00:27:22,339 --> 00:27:22,859
[SPEAKER_00] kod vas.

522
00:27:22,859 --> 00:27:24,359
[SPEAKER_01] Sve što oni tu radi,

523
00:27:24,359 --> 00:27:25,220
[SPEAKER_01] to i vi radite,

524
00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] samo što je kod njih

525
00:27:26,059 --> 00:27:26,759
[SPEAKER_01] puno više.

526
00:27:26,759 --> 00:27:28,799
[SPEAKER_01] I oni imaju puno učenika

527
00:27:28,799 --> 00:27:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] i onda to je njihova

528
00:27:30,039 --> 00:27:30,839
[SPEAKER_01] radna snaga.

529
00:27:30,839 --> 00:27:32,380
[SPEAKER_01] A mi tamo radimo sve.

530
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo svinje,

531
00:27:33,619 --> 00:27:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] imamo kokoši,

532
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] imamo zečeve,

533
00:27:35,279 --> 00:27:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] imamo patke,

534
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:39,319
[SPEAKER_01] onda imamo kokoši,

535
00:27:39,319 --> 00:27:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] imamo jaja,

536
00:27:40,019 --> 00:27:42,180
[SPEAKER_01] od toga meso,

537
00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,200
[SPEAKER_01] nešto prodamo,

538
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:44,140
[SPEAKER_01] jaja prodamo,

539
00:27:44,140 --> 00:27:46,119
[SPEAKER_01] dobar dio prodamo,

540
00:27:46,119 --> 00:27:47,059
[SPEAKER_01] jer imamo više

541
00:27:47,059 --> 00:27:48,059
[SPEAKER_01] kokoša radi,

542
00:27:48,059 --> 00:27:48,880
[SPEAKER_01] da možemo povedati,

543
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja je u selu,

544
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:50,839
[SPEAKER_01] ne ima nitko kokoša.

545
00:27:50,839 --> 00:27:52,160
[SPEAKER_01] I onda,

546
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] svinje isto je nešto,

547
00:27:54,519 --> 00:27:55,259
[SPEAKER_01] mi pojedemo,

548
00:27:55,259 --> 00:27:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] a dobar dio prodamo.

549
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:59,180
[SPEAKER_01] Da imamo nekakvu financiju,

550
00:27:59,180 --> 00:28:00,240
[SPEAKER_01] nešto,

551
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:00,859
[SPEAKER_01] moramo se neći...

552
00:28:00,859 --> 00:28:01,599
[SPEAKER_00] Samo drživost,

553
00:28:01,599 --> 00:28:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] da je najekonomičnije moguće

554
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:05,180
[SPEAKER_01] funkcionirati.

555
00:28:05,180 --> 00:28:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je moguće,

556
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,180
[SPEAKER_01] da možemo živjeti,

557
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:09,799
[SPEAKER_01] jer da čekaš da sve dobiješ

558
00:28:09,799 --> 00:28:11,279
[SPEAKER_01] od nekoga milostinju,

559
00:28:11,279 --> 00:28:11,839
[SPEAKER_01] malo ne.

560
00:28:11,839 --> 00:28:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] Malo će biti teže.

561
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:13,759
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da,

562
00:28:13,759 --> 00:28:15,319
[SPEAKER_00] pa mislim i u konačnici

563
00:28:15,319 --> 00:28:16,579
[SPEAKER_00] onda su ljudi motivirani,

564
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] pomagat kada vidi

565
00:28:17,599 --> 00:28:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se ono što daruju

566
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,059
[SPEAKER_00] ulaže na jedan dobar način

567
00:28:21,059 --> 00:28:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] i da svi rastu,

568
00:28:22,019 --> 00:28:23,799
[SPEAKER_00] da se ljudi osamostaljuju,

569
00:28:23,799 --> 00:28:24,700
[SPEAKER_00] da...

570
00:28:24,700 --> 00:28:25,700
[SPEAKER_01] To je kod nas tako,

571
00:28:25,700 --> 00:28:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] od početka mi smo tako krenule

572
00:28:27,599 --> 00:28:30,200
[SPEAKER_01] i na neki način,

573
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:32,160
[SPEAKER_01] na početku malo su nas

574
00:28:32,160 --> 00:28:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] čudno gledali,

575
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:34,859
[SPEAKER_01] pa zašto mi toliko radimo?

576
00:28:34,859 --> 00:28:36,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mi kaže,

577
00:28:36,079 --> 00:28:37,640
[SPEAKER_01] zašto vi ne možete uzeti šofera,

578
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu ga platiti.

579
00:28:39,319 --> 00:28:40,339
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto i ta slika

580
00:28:40,339 --> 00:28:41,119
[SPEAKER_00] nekakva bila

581
00:28:41,119 --> 00:28:42,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz kolonijalnih vremena

582
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] o bijelim ljudima,

583
00:28:45,319 --> 00:28:46,799
[SPEAKER_00] da su to oni koji imaju šofere,

584
00:28:46,799 --> 00:28:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne rade.

585
00:28:48,059 --> 00:28:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] U stvari,

586
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] vi ste donijeli jednu potpuno

587
00:28:50,559 --> 00:28:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] drugu sliku,

588
00:28:51,079 --> 00:28:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] misjonari,

589
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] onih bijelih ljudi

590
00:28:53,539 --> 00:28:54,720
[SPEAKER_00] koji su s njima

591
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] radi njih.

592
00:28:55,779 --> 00:28:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] iz ljubavi preva njima.

593
00:28:57,980 --> 00:29:00,140
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako imate šofera,

594
00:29:00,140 --> 00:29:01,680
[SPEAKER_01] morate ga platiti pošteno.

595
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,299
[SPEAKER_01] Da, naravno.

596
00:29:02,299 --> 00:29:03,140
[SPEAKER_01] To nije da mu date

597
00:29:03,140 --> 00:29:04,220
[SPEAKER_01] nekakvu milostinju,

598
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:06,200
[SPEAKER_01] ja to sebi ne mogu dozvoliti.

599
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:06,700
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

600
00:29:06,700 --> 00:29:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan dan,

601
00:29:07,519 --> 00:29:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] koliko on čovjek gubi,

602
00:29:09,119 --> 00:29:10,319
[SPEAKER_01] da je sa mnom na putu

603
00:29:10,319 --> 00:29:10,799
[SPEAKER_01] ili to,

604
00:29:10,799 --> 00:29:12,299
[SPEAKER_01] tako da po tome

605
00:29:12,299 --> 00:29:14,140
[SPEAKER_01] drugi možda imaju šofere,

606
00:29:14,140 --> 00:29:14,859
[SPEAKER_01] uzmu nekoga

607
00:29:14,859 --> 00:29:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] iz svoje obitelji,

608
00:29:15,980 --> 00:29:17,180
[SPEAKER_01] ti domaći sestre,

609
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:18,660
[SPEAKER_01] po kojemu daju

610
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] mrvicu.

611
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nije,

612
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:22,240
[SPEAKER_01] da mene je ni pošteno.

613
00:29:22,240 --> 00:29:22,779
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

614
00:29:22,779 --> 00:29:23,980
[SPEAKER_01] Jer on ima svoji obitelj

615
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:25,759
[SPEAKER_01] i to dajmo kako mu spada.

616
00:29:25,759 --> 00:29:27,019
[SPEAKER_01] Onaj minimum koji bu mu,

617
00:29:27,019 --> 00:29:28,099
[SPEAKER_01] da radi negdje

618
00:29:28,099 --> 00:29:29,640
[SPEAKER_01] u nekoj kao i državnoj službi,

619
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:30,940
[SPEAKER_01] taj minimum koji bi dobio,

620
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi mu to došlo.

621
00:29:33,420 --> 00:29:33,819
[SPEAKER_00] Vi ste,

622
00:29:33,819 --> 00:29:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad govorimo o osposobljavanju

623
00:29:36,500 --> 00:29:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] za život te djece,

624
00:29:37,880 --> 00:29:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

625
00:29:38,579 --> 00:29:40,099
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo imali priliku

626
00:29:40,099 --> 00:29:42,380
[SPEAKER_00] posjetiti jednu vašu štićenicu,

627
00:29:42,380 --> 00:29:42,900
[SPEAKER_00] bivšu,

628
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] koja je krojačica,

629
00:29:44,039 --> 00:29:44,400
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

630
00:29:44,400 --> 00:29:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji ste...

631
00:29:45,420 --> 00:29:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čujte,

632
00:29:46,619 --> 00:29:47,660
[SPEAKER_01] ima ih puno,

633
00:29:47,660 --> 00:29:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] koji su završili nekakav zanad,

634
00:29:50,220 --> 00:29:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] nekoji su završili škole.

635
00:29:53,119 --> 00:29:55,140
[SPEAKER_01] I neki koji su dobro učili,

636
00:29:55,140 --> 00:29:56,259
[SPEAKER_01] pa idu na školu,

637
00:29:56,259 --> 00:29:56,759
[SPEAKER_01] pa dalje,

638
00:29:56,759 --> 00:29:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] to je manjina,

639
00:29:57,859 --> 00:30:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] oni koji mi možemo i dalje školovat,

640
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:02,220
[SPEAKER_01] završi fakultet i to.

641
00:30:02,220 --> 00:30:03,859
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo i takvih,

642
00:30:03,859 --> 00:30:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] imamo oni koji završavaju

643
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] nekakav zanad,

644
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] jedna djevojka koja je,

645
00:30:09,420 --> 00:30:11,039
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

646
00:30:11,039 --> 00:30:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] to je tako,

647
00:30:12,079 --> 00:30:13,279
[SPEAKER_01] čudna priča,

648
00:30:13,279 --> 00:30:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je Boži plan.

649
00:30:15,119 --> 00:30:17,200
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo mi došli na sjever gore,

650
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:20,140
[SPEAKER_01] mi nismo imali u planu

651
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] uzeti djecu.

652
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] u biro kad ste došli gore.

653
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,220
[SPEAKER_01] U biro kad smo došli,

654
00:30:23,220 --> 00:30:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] da.

655
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo imali u planu

656
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:25,819
[SPEAKER_01] uzeti djecu.

657
00:30:25,819 --> 00:30:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] Imali smo,

658
00:30:26,539 --> 00:30:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] prvo nam je bilo bolesnici.

659
00:30:28,619 --> 00:30:30,039
[SPEAKER_01] Otvoriti ambulantu,

660
00:30:30,039 --> 00:30:32,240
[SPEAKER_01] osigurati besplatnu pomoć.

661
00:30:32,619 --> 00:30:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] nismo mi imali nikakvu ambulantu,

662
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo živjeli u toj okrugloj kućici,

663
00:30:36,380 --> 00:30:37,680
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo dvije prostorije,

664
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,759
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo garažu,

665
00:30:38,759 --> 00:30:41,180
[SPEAKER_01] ali ljudi kad su čuli sestre su tu,

666
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:42,839
[SPEAKER_01] oni su dolazili kod nas

667
00:30:42,839 --> 00:30:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] na liječenje.

668
00:30:44,119 --> 00:30:44,819
[SPEAKER_01] I vidite,

669
00:30:44,819 --> 00:30:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] to vam je

670
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] taj narod

671
00:30:47,599 --> 00:30:48,019
[SPEAKER_01] i sad

672
00:30:48,019 --> 00:30:49,440
[SPEAKER_01] jedan razgovor.

673
00:30:49,839 --> 00:30:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] došla je žena,

674
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa kaže mi,

675
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] ja u tom selu ima

676
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:53,240
[SPEAKER_01] zličana ambulanta.

677
00:30:53,240 --> 00:30:54,900
[SPEAKER_01] Mogli ste ići tamo?

678
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:55,579
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

679
00:30:55,579 --> 00:30:56,420
[SPEAKER_01] daleko vam je.

680
00:30:56,420 --> 00:30:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da,

681
00:30:57,619 --> 00:30:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] kaže,

682
00:30:58,000 --> 00:31:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali ta i ta žena je bila kod vas

683
00:31:00,619 --> 00:31:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] i onda je dobila ljekove,

684
00:31:01,960 --> 00:31:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] njezino djete je dobro

685
00:31:03,519 --> 00:31:05,279
[SPEAKER_01] i onda je ona meni rekla,

686
00:31:05,279 --> 00:31:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] idite vi kod sistara,

687
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] tamo ćete dobiti i ljekove,

688
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,319
[SPEAKER_01] a imate i molitvu.

689
00:31:09,319 --> 00:31:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ljudi dolazi kod sistara,

690
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:14,420
[SPEAKER_01] to koliko zbog ljekova,

691
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:15,779
[SPEAKER_01] još više radi molitve.

692
00:31:15,779 --> 00:31:17,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sestre mole za njih,

693
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,759
[SPEAKER_01] to su oni sigurni.

694
00:31:18,759 --> 00:31:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] I onda mi nismo imali,

695
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] opće nam je bilo u svijesti za djecu.

696
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,259
[SPEAKER_01] Nemamo gdje,

697
00:31:25,259 --> 00:31:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] nemamo vlastiti u kuću,

698
00:31:26,460 --> 00:31:27,180
[SPEAKER_01] nemamo ništa.

699
00:31:27,180 --> 00:31:29,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ali pojavila se tako jedna djevojka

700
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:32,759
[SPEAKER_01] u selu koja je završila osnovnu školu.

701
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,660
[SPEAKER_01] njih su dvije sestre

702
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:37,119
[SPEAKER_01] i živi sa bakom koja je gubavka.

703
00:31:37,119 --> 00:31:38,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ona ima te posljedice gube,

704
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,660
[SPEAKER_01] nema sve prste,

705
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:41,140
[SPEAKER_01] na nogama nima ni jednog.

706
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:42,359
[SPEAKER_01] I tako.

707
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] I sad baka kaže,

708
00:31:44,119 --> 00:31:45,180
[SPEAKER_01] to je već je djevojka,

709
00:31:45,180 --> 00:31:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] obično te djevojke ostaju trudne,

710
00:31:47,119 --> 00:31:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] pre rano,

711
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:50,140
[SPEAKER_01] ona nju ne može držati,

712
00:31:50,140 --> 00:31:51,519
[SPEAKER_01] jer zna šta će se dogoditi.

713
00:31:51,519 --> 00:31:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kaže mala,

714
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,119
[SPEAKER_01] ona će ići u školu,

715
00:31:54,119 --> 00:31:55,700
[SPEAKER_01] a ona će ići u paraku,

716
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] to je grad,

717
00:31:56,880 --> 00:32:00,299
[SPEAKER_01] tražit će ona ko će nju primiti

718
00:32:00,299 --> 00:32:01,619
[SPEAKER_01] da ona ide u školu.

719
00:32:01,619 --> 00:32:03,619
[SPEAKER_01] a žene u selu znaju

720
00:32:03,619 --> 00:32:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] ko će ju primiti.

721
00:32:05,059 --> 00:32:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] I one su došli nas moliti sestro,

722
00:32:07,680 --> 00:32:08,740
[SPEAKER_01] daj primite ju,

723
00:32:08,740 --> 00:32:09,599
[SPEAKER_01] daj pomozite ju,

724
00:32:09,599 --> 00:32:11,019
[SPEAKER_01] samo nek ne ide u grad.

725
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:13,299
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo mi tako,

726
00:32:13,299 --> 00:32:14,940
[SPEAKER_01] pa nema ko ću i smijestiti.

727
00:32:14,940 --> 00:32:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] Onako je dvije sobe, da.

728
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:19,900
[SPEAKER_01] A onda je došlo iz sela,

729
00:32:19,900 --> 00:32:20,559
[SPEAKER_01] ima su rekli,

730
00:32:20,559 --> 00:32:21,420
[SPEAKER_01] evo taj čovjek,

731
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,039
[SPEAKER_01] on ima jednu sobu praznu,

732
00:32:23,039 --> 00:32:24,480
[SPEAKER_01] one nek budu kod vas,

733
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] ali tamo nek idu samo spavat.

734
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:30,440
[SPEAKER_01] Tako smo primili neki desetak djevojčica,

735
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] i one su išli tamo spavat,

736
00:32:31,900 --> 00:32:33,779
[SPEAKER_01] i kod nas su bili lepo cijeli dana,

737
00:32:33,779 --> 00:32:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] već je u deset sati,

738
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad završe učenje.

739
00:32:36,779 --> 00:32:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] Onda i sestre prate tamo,

740
00:32:38,579 --> 00:32:39,160
[SPEAKER_01] i vrati.

741
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] Tako smo krenuli mi primati djecu,

742
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa vidimo da je dobro.

743
00:32:44,119 --> 00:32:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] I sad poslije ona je završila

744
00:32:46,099 --> 00:32:47,259
[SPEAKER_01] dio srednje škole,

745
00:32:47,259 --> 00:32:49,640
[SPEAKER_01] pa su im je poslala u gostiteljsku.

746
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je završila u gostiteljsku školu,

747
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:55,279
[SPEAKER_01] i dan kad je ona primala diplom,

748
00:32:55,279 --> 00:32:57,720
[SPEAKER_01] ona je toliko plakala.

749
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da.

750
00:32:59,519 --> 00:33:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] I njezina mlađa sestra,

751
00:33:00,900 --> 00:33:02,319
[SPEAKER_01] koja je isto već bila kod nas,

752
00:33:02,319 --> 00:33:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže,

753
00:33:03,380 --> 00:33:05,160
[SPEAKER_01] nikad ne bi nitko mislio,

754
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:06,759
[SPEAKER_01] da bismo mi mogli doći

755
00:33:06,759 --> 00:33:08,740
[SPEAKER_01] doći da netko od nas primi diplomu,

756
00:33:08,740 --> 00:33:09,980
[SPEAKER_01] da nije bilo vas.

757
00:33:09,980 --> 00:33:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] I u stvari tak je istina.

758
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:15,400
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, tako smo mi krenuli s tom djecom,

759
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:18,740
[SPEAKER_01] i puno se pomaže toj djeci,

760
00:33:18,740 --> 00:33:20,779
[SPEAKER_01] i onda tako završavaju školu,

761
00:33:20,779 --> 00:33:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] ne, poslije se zaposlala,

762
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,819
[SPEAKER_01] radila u hotelu.

763
00:33:23,819 --> 00:33:26,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, ima, otvaraju se opcije za budućnost.

764
00:33:26,319 --> 00:33:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

765
00:33:26,559 --> 00:33:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni su, ljudi su budućnost,

766
00:33:28,599 --> 00:33:30,180
[SPEAKER_00] koji idu dalje,

767
00:33:30,180 --> 00:33:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji izidu iz siromaštva,

768
00:33:31,579 --> 00:33:32,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji rade sami,

769
00:33:32,579 --> 00:33:33,859
[SPEAKER_00] koji rade sami za sebe.

770
00:33:33,859 --> 00:33:34,279
[SPEAKER_00] Sigurno.

771
00:33:34,279 --> 00:33:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to je,

772
00:33:35,079 --> 00:33:36,599
[SPEAKER_01] više ne ovisi ni o kome,

773
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,700
[SPEAKER_01] i ima takvih

774
00:33:37,700 --> 00:33:39,279
[SPEAKER_01] priličan broj.

775
00:33:39,279 --> 00:33:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] Djece.

776
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mene, u birovu,

777
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što ste rekli,

778
00:33:41,619 --> 00:33:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] da je ova mama rekla,

779
00:33:43,099 --> 00:33:43,640
[SPEAKER_00] da je došla

780
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] radi ljekova

781
00:33:45,119 --> 00:33:46,019
[SPEAKER_00] i radi molitve,

782
00:33:46,019 --> 00:33:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] meni tako odzvanja još,

783
00:33:49,500 --> 00:33:50,720
[SPEAKER_00] ono, u srcu,

784
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] ta jutarnja molitva,

785
00:33:52,619 --> 00:33:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] koju vi imate,

786
00:33:53,319 --> 00:33:55,240
[SPEAKER_00] kako divno sestre pjevaju,

787
00:33:55,240 --> 00:33:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali i kako bubnjaju.

788
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] A be,

789
00:33:57,480 --> 00:33:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] čujte,

790
00:33:58,119 --> 00:33:59,180
[SPEAKER_00] ne može se kod nas

791
