792
00:34:00,799 --> 00:34:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

793
00:34:01,019 --> 00:34:03,380
[SPEAKER_01] mora biti uvijek popraćeno

794
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] sa instrumentima.

795
00:34:05,059 --> 00:34:06,740
[SPEAKER_01] To su ti naši instrumenti,

796
00:34:06,740 --> 00:34:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo ako je nekakav blagdan,

797
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] što ja vidim ovdje,

798
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] završi se i časoslov,

799
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] 10-15 minuta,

800
00:34:14,599 --> 00:34:15,360
[SPEAKER_01] ovrglavi,

801
00:34:15,360 --> 00:34:17,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali kod nas je pola sata.

802
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:18,420
[SPEAKER_01] da, da, da.

803
00:34:18,420 --> 00:34:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] Misli, uzmemo vrijeme,

804
00:34:19,920 --> 00:34:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer časoslov se pjeva.

805
00:34:21,699 --> 00:34:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] To su psalmi za pjevanje

806
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:24,280
