00:34:27,260 --> 00:34:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

811
00:34:29,139 --> 00:34:31,099
[SPEAKER_01] nama je osobno zadovoljstvo

812
00:34:31,099 --> 00:34:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] i jedna prilika

813
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,079
