814
00:34:34,079 --> 00:34:34,820
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

815
00:34:34,820 --> 00:34:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da...

816
00:34:36,639 --> 00:34:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da, molitva kao odmor,

817
00:34:38,019 --> 00:34:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] pa da.

818
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] Imala jednu priliku,

819
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:40,699
[SPEAKER_01] gore,

820
00:34:40,699 --> 00:34:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] što je bilo u Virov,

821
00:34:42,539 --> 00:34:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] imali smo misu,

822
00:34:44,539 --> 00:34:44,920
[SPEAKER_01] negdje,

823
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,639
[SPEAKER_01] oko poodne

824
