[SPEAKER_01] i sad,

825
00:34:47,019 --> 00:34:48,599
[SPEAKER_01] taman mi sad treba početi

826
00:34:48,599 --> 00:34:50,360
[SPEAKER_01] i došli su sa nekim,

827
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:51,679
[SPEAKER_01] sa djecom i to.

828
00:34:51,679 --> 00:34:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] Veli se strašno,

829
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] šta sad redim?

830
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] Odi, daj im ono,

831
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] prvo što im je sad hitno,

832
00:34:56,019 --> 00:34:57,380
[SPEAKER_01] vidiš temperaturu i to,

833
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] daj djetetu prvu pomoć

834
