840
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,639
[SPEAKER_01] I mi je rekla,

841
00:35:08,639 --> 00:35:09,699
[SPEAKER_01] ne, idite vi na misu.

842
00:35:09,699 --> 00:35:12,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je pomolit se za moj djete.

843
00:35:12,699 --> 00:35:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] I idite vi na misu,

844
