850
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:23,179
[SPEAKER_01] A idite vi najprije na misu.

851
00:35:23,179 --> 00:35:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] To je na neki način

852
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:29,019
[SPEAKER_01] iza nas svjedočanstvo

853
