874
00:35:58,039 --> 00:35:58,840
[SPEAKER_01] teče tako.

875
00:36:00,340 --> 00:36:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan je isprogramiran,

876
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] bez da ga mi programiramo.

877
00:36:03,039 --> 00:36:03,739
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

878
00:36:03,739 --> 00:36:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo što kažete,

879
00:36:05,019 --> 00:36:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] to je doista,

880
