883
00:36:09,579 --> 00:36:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] zajedno sa vamo,

884
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] sa sestrama.

885
00:36:13,219 --> 00:36:14,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

886
00:36:14,119 --> 00:36:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] doista ta,

887
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:15,539
