889
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] objektivno,

890
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] u teškim vremenskim uvjetima,

891
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:21,260
[SPEAKER_00] vruće je,

892
00:36:21,260 --> 00:36:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] nemaš konfor

893
00:36:22,739 --> 00:36:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji si nauči ovdje sve.

894
00:36:24,039 --> 00:36:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali,

895
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,440
[SPEAKER_00] z druhe strane,

896
00:36:25,440 --> 00:36:26,840
[SPEAKER_00] stalno je radost,

897
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:28,500
[SPEAKER_00] smijek tih sestara,

898
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,579
[SPEAKER_00] veselje na večer

899
00:36:29,579 --> 00:36:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] kad se sjednu,

900
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,000
