901
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,539
[SPEAKER_00] poslije molitve kad se priča.

902
00:36:32,539 --> 00:36:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle,

903
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedna takva radost,

904
