[SPEAKER_00] da je nadnaravna,

906
00:36:37,139 --> 00:36:38,179
[SPEAKER_00] nije naravna.

907
00:36:38,179 --> 00:36:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] U stvari,

908
00:36:38,539 --> 00:36:41,380
