[SPEAKER_01] tu kod nas,

911
00:36:44,659 --> 00:36:47,239
[SPEAKER_01] tamo gdje ima radosti,

912
00:36:47,239 --> 00:36:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] ima života.

913
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:49,340
[SPEAKER_01] I onda umor,

914
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,380
[SPEAKER_01] kad radite,

915
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] umorni ste,

916
00:36:51,480 --> 00:36:52,420
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako ima radosti,

917
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:53,559
[SPEAKER_01] pola umora je manje.

918
00:36:53,559 --> 00:36:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] A ono kad je tmurno,

919
