[SPEAKER_01] svak za sebe,

920
00:36:56,980 --> 00:36:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način radi

921
00:36:58,739 --> 00:37:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] i možda gunđao u sebi,

922
00:37:00,239 --> 00:37:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] onda i umor duplo veći.

923
00:37:02,340 --> 00:37:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što,

924
00:37:03,159 --> 00:37:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] ono što,

925
00:37:03,980 --> 00:37:06,420
[SPEAKER_00] nekako s jedne strane,

926
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] ta radost

927
00:37:08,059 --> 00:37:09,320
[SPEAKER_00] i se stara vaših

928
