[SPEAKER_00] kad ih čovjek susreće,

930
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,559
[SPEAKER_00] tako malo imaju,

931
00:37:13,559 --> 00:37:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] a imaju tu jednu pozitivan odnos,

932
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] sreću zbog maloga,

933
00:37:17,099 --> 00:37:18,280
[SPEAKER_00] zbog bilo čega,

934
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] dobro ga raduje radost.

935
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:21,719
[SPEAKER_01] Oni se raduju

936
00:37:21,719 --> 00:37:22,219
[SPEAKER_01] i recimo,

937
00:37:22,219 --> 00:37:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] na neki način,

938
