[SPEAKER_01] oni su zahvalni.

939
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] Zahvalni su Bogu,

940
00:37:27,539 --> 00:37:29,559
[SPEAKER_01] vjernici i nevjernici.

941
00:37:29,559 --> 00:37:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, to je zanimljivo.

942
00:37:31,199 --> 00:37:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] malo uberu

943
