[SPEAKER_01] jedna pouka,

952
00:37:43,159 --> 00:37:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi,

953
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,719
[SPEAKER_01] što da,

954
00:37:45,719 --> 00:37:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] Bog,

955
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:46,519
[SPEAKER_01] to je dosta.

956
00:37:47,199 --> 00:37:50,059
[SPEAKER_01] i hajde kako se živi.

957
00:37:50,059 --> 00:37:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da,

958
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,659
