[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

967
00:38:01,059 --> 00:38:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] do vašeg samostana,

968
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] do vaše kuće,

969
00:38:05,119 --> 00:38:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] smo vidjeli fotografiju

970
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] prvog svećenika

971
00:38:08,039 --> 00:38:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] zaređenog Beninca,

972
00:38:10,139 --> 00:38:10,420
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

973
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,900
[SPEAKER_00] domaćeg čovjeka.

974
00:38:11,900 --> 00:38:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali iznenadno me,

975
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] to je u stvari tek,

976
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:16,360
[SPEAKER_00] nije prošlo niti sto godina

977
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:16,860
[SPEAKER_00] od kada je,

978
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] to je u stvari jako nova,

979
00:38:18,539 --> 00:38:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] nova,

980
00:38:19,699 --> 00:38:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] katoličanstvo je novo

981
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:22,019
[SPEAKER_00] u Beninu,

982
00:38:22,019 --> 00:38:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] je li?

983
00:38:22,199 --> 00:38:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] U Beninu,

984
00:38:22,739 --> 00:38:25,159
[SPEAKER_01] to je 150 godina.

985
00:38:25,159 --> 00:38:26,480
[SPEAKER_01] To vam je,

986
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:27,440
[SPEAKER_01] to je ništa.

987
00:38:27,440 --> 00:38:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] Za 150 godina,

988
00:38:29,239 --> 00:38:30,400
[SPEAKER_01] što se može napraviti?

989
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] To je dole,

990
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,139
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

991
00:38:32,139 --> 00:38:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] južni dio,

992
00:38:32,860 --> 00:38:34,139
[SPEAKER_01] 150 godina.

993
00:38:34,139 --> 00:38:35,500
[SPEAKER_01] A gore na sjeveru

994
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] je puno kasnije.

995
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,860
[SPEAKER_01] Sjever je puno siromašniji

996
00:38:38,860 --> 00:38:40,280
[SPEAKER_01] i

997
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] neće vam nitko gore ići.

998
00:38:43,679 --> 00:38:44,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ne želi,

999
00:38:44,599 --> 00:38:44,940
[SPEAKER_01] aha,

1000
00:38:45,159 --> 00:38:46,940
[SPEAKER_01] neće vam nitko gore ići.

1001
00:38:46,940 --> 00:38:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] Kad smo mi išli na dogovor

1002
00:38:48,639 --> 00:38:49,739
[SPEAKER_01] sa našim biskupom

1003
00:38:49,739 --> 00:38:51,320
[SPEAKER_01] gore za biro,

1004
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] to je dakle,

1005
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] te grad na sjeveru gore,

1006
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] da,

1007
00:38:54,699 --> 00:38:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] i sad

1008
00:38:55,539 --> 00:38:58,059
[SPEAKER_01] bila je naša poglavarica

1009
00:38:58,059 --> 00:38:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] odavdje iz Hrvatske,

1010
00:38:59,199 --> 00:39:00,980
[SPEAKER_01] da vidimo,

1011
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] još nije to bilo

1012
00:39:02,139 --> 00:39:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] 100% sigurno,

1013
00:39:03,199 --> 00:39:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali da,

1014
00:39:03,659 --> 00:39:04,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa da vidimo,

1015
00:39:04,860 --> 00:39:06,900
[SPEAKER_01] kud bi nas biskup stavio,

1016
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] kad je već to tu,

1017
00:39:07,940 --> 00:39:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] no je rekao,

1018
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:09,179
[SPEAKER_01] dobro,

1019
00:39:09,179 --> 00:39:10,739
[SPEAKER_01] sad će on malo se raspitati,

1020
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] ima on 3-4 mjesta,

1021
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] koja bi ponudio sestrama,

1022
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:16,940
[SPEAKER_01] tako,

1023
00:39:16,940 --> 00:39:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] sad,

1024
00:39:17,559 --> 00:39:20,219
[SPEAKER_01] gdje bi mi,

1025
00:39:20,219 --> 00:39:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] pitao on,

1026
00:39:21,599 --> 00:39:22,980
[SPEAKER_01] i onda na koncu on kaže,

1027
00:39:22,980 --> 00:39:24,019
[SPEAKER_01] da,

1028
00:39:24,019 --> 00:39:26,179
[SPEAKER_01] pa sve sestre,

1029
00:39:26,179 --> 00:39:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] što dolaze gore,

1030
00:39:27,539 --> 00:39:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] sve bi htjeli ostati u gradu.

1031
00:39:31,619 --> 00:39:32,320
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ja,

1032
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] oče biskupe,

1033
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] naproti,

1034
00:39:34,039 --> 00:39:35,340
[SPEAKER_01] mi ne želimo ostati u gradu.

1035
00:39:35,340 --> 00:39:37,679
[SPEAKER_01] Eme,

1036
00:39:37,679 --> 00:39:38,199
[SPEAKER_01] ni glede,

1037
00:39:38,199 --> 00:39:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] čudno.

1038
00:39:38,659 --> 00:39:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem ja,

1039
00:39:40,039 --> 00:39:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] nas grad uopće ne privlači,

1040
00:39:42,059 --> 00:39:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] mi možemo ići na selo.

1041
00:39:44,199 --> 00:39:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] E, kažem,

1042
00:39:45,059 --> 00:39:45,719
[SPEAKER_01] ako je tako,

1043
00:39:45,719 --> 00:39:46,239
[SPEAKER_01] onda je,

1044
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] mi je već lakše.

1045
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:48,300
[SPEAKER_00] Da, pa da.

1046
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:51,179
[SPEAKER_01] I onda nas je odveo najprije u to selo,

1047
00:39:51,179 --> 00:39:52,780
[SPEAKER_01] gdje smo se naselili u biro,

1048
00:39:52,780 --> 00:39:54,199
[SPEAKER_01] on je,

1049
00:39:54,199 --> 00:39:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] na veće smo nijedje razgovarali u 6 sati,

1050
00:39:56,619 --> 00:40:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] i ujutro smo ona imali nekakav dogovor,

1051
00:40:00,420 --> 00:40:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] za 9 ili 10 sati,

1052
00:40:02,260 --> 00:40:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] od malih crkvica,

1053
00:40:05,139 --> 00:40:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali crkva je bila puna,

1054
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:07,760
[SPEAKER_01] svećenika nije bilo tu.

1055
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:10,300
[SPEAKER_01] On je se dogovorio,

1056
00:40:10,300 --> 00:40:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam s kim,

1057
00:40:10,980 --> 00:40:12,900
[SPEAKER_01] da sestri će doći.

1058
00:40:12,900 --> 00:40:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] Maltene,

1059
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] cijelo selo je došlo,

1060
00:40:15,139 --> 00:40:16,760
[SPEAKER_01] što muslimani,

1061
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:17,699
[SPEAKER_01] što animisti,

1062
00:40:17,699 --> 00:40:19,139
[SPEAKER_01] koliko vjernika je bilo,

1063
00:40:19,139 --> 00:40:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] oni su svi došli,

1064
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] jer sestre dolazi.

1065
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:24,119
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo se tu dogovarali,

1066
00:40:24,119 --> 00:40:24,639
[SPEAKER_01] oćemo,

1067
00:40:24,639 --> 00:40:25,219
[SPEAKER_01] nećemo,

1068
00:40:25,219 --> 00:40:25,719
[SPEAKER_01] sam rekla,

1069
00:40:25,719 --> 00:40:26,639
[SPEAKER_01] ako dolazimo,

1070
00:40:26,639 --> 00:40:28,019
[SPEAKER_01] oćemo naš teren.

1071
00:40:28,019 --> 00:40:30,380
[SPEAKER_01] Onda nam ne prireklimo,

1072
00:40:30,420 --> 00:40:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] što je kupiti.

1073
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:31,300
[SPEAKER_01] Sam rekla,

1074
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:32,179
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne kupujem teren.

1075
00:40:32,179 --> 00:40:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vi nas trebate,

1076
00:40:34,079 --> 00:40:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] vi nama dajte zemlju.

1077
00:40:35,239 --> 00:40:37,260
[SPEAKER_01] A drugo vas ne tražimo,

1078
00:40:37,260 --> 00:40:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] samo zemlju.

1079
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] A sam rekla,

1080
00:40:39,079 --> 00:40:40,900
[SPEAKER_01] ima župski teren,

1081
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:41,820
[SPEAKER_01] koji je jako velik,

1082
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:43,039
[SPEAKER_01] možemo vam dati,

1083
00:40:43,039 --> 00:40:43,400
[SPEAKER_01] odati,

1084
00:40:43,400 --> 00:40:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] rekla sam,

1085
00:40:43,920 --> 00:40:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] neću.

1086
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] Oći u moj vlastiti teren.

1087
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] Što je župsko,

1088
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:48,539
[SPEAKER_01] to je župsko.

1089
00:40:48,539 --> 00:40:51,059
[SPEAKER_01] Zemlja je prazna,

1090
00:40:51,059 --> 00:40:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] nima ništa.

1091
00:40:51,559 --> 00:40:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] No da.

1092
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] I on srkli,

1093
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:53,940
[SPEAKER_01] nema problema.

1094
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:54,719
[SPEAKER_01] Za kratko vreme

1095
00:40:54,719 --> 00:40:55,519
[SPEAKER_01] se oni nam rekli,

1096
00:40:55,519 --> 00:40:56,199
[SPEAKER_01] da su nam dali,

1097
00:40:56,199 --> 00:40:58,300
[SPEAKER_01] imamo dva hektara zemlje,

1098
00:40:58,300 --> 00:40:59,360
[SPEAKER_01] tu i tu.

1099
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:00,480
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono gdje koje je ubiro

1100
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] ugrađeni,

1101
00:41:01,179 --> 00:41:02,320
[SPEAKER_01] je li to ono gdje je sad ugrađeno?

1102
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:02,960
[SPEAKER_01] Sad naše,

1103
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:05,139
[SPEAKER_01] sad je to puno više nego dva,

1104
00:41:05,139 --> 00:41:07,219
[SPEAKER_01] sad je više od tri hektara tu.

1105
00:41:07,219 --> 00:41:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] I onda smo poslije dogovarali se,

1106
00:41:10,699 --> 00:41:11,460
[SPEAKER_01] pregovarali,

1107
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:11,820
[SPEAKER_01] tako,

1108
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] rekla sam,

1109
00:41:12,099 --> 00:41:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] ja ne mogu graditi,

1110
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:15,860
[SPEAKER_01] biti dole i graditi tu kuću,

1111
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:16,860
[SPEAKER_01] a nema ni sredstava.

1112
00:41:16,860 --> 00:41:18,900
[SPEAKER_01] Onda je biskup nam napravio

1113
00:41:18,900 --> 00:41:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] tu okruglu kuću,

1114
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:20,699
[SPEAKER_01] što sam pričala,

1115
00:41:20,699 --> 00:41:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] malo ju uredio,

1116
00:41:21,659 --> 00:41:23,099
[SPEAKER_01] onda smo mi došli.

1117
00:41:23,099 --> 00:41:25,940
[SPEAKER_01] Pojave ceja u BNV još uvijek ne postoji.

1118
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:27,320
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da.

1119
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:27,900
[SPEAKER_01] Smo došli,

1120
00:41:27,900 --> 00:41:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] da,

1121
00:41:28,139 --> 00:41:29,199
[SPEAKER_01] onda vam pokazali kuću,

1122
00:41:29,199 --> 00:41:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] sve su uredili,

1123
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:31,260
[SPEAKER_01] čisto,

1124
00:41:31,719 --> 00:41:32,719
[SPEAKER_01] možete živjeti tu.

1125
00:41:32,719 --> 00:41:33,840
[SPEAKER_01] Samo obišla sve.

1126
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jel vam se sviđa?

1127
00:41:37,019 --> 00:41:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Može.

1128
00:41:37,579 --> 00:41:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] Možete biti,

1129
00:41:38,739 --> 00:41:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] pa možete sad doći.

1130
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:40,980
[SPEAKER_01] Žemija može.

1131
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:44,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna je žena bila s nama.

1132
00:41:44,019 --> 00:41:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže mi ja njoj,

1133
00:41:45,619 --> 00:41:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] neka mi pokaže

1134
00:41:46,659 --> 00:41:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] da trebam ići u WC.

1135
00:41:47,739 --> 00:41:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Že nema.

1136
00:41:50,460 --> 00:41:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] Epa,

1137
00:41:51,559 --> 00:41:53,019
[SPEAKER_01] jel mogu ja živjeti bez WC?

1138
00:41:53,019 --> 00:41:53,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne mogu.

1139
00:41:53,659 --> 00:41:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kaže uopće njima,

1140
00:41:56,079 --> 00:41:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] to ne prilo na pamet.

1141
00:41:57,460 --> 00:42:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zanimljivo mi je to

1142
00:42:00,659 --> 00:42:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] kako ste vi u stvari,

1143
00:42:01,519 --> 00:42:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] koristili tu

1144
00:42:03,139 --> 00:42:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] danas ono

1145
00:42:04,119 --> 00:42:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] svi projekti

1146
00:42:05,239 --> 00:42:06,079
[SPEAKER_00] učinkoviti

1147
00:42:06,079 --> 00:42:07,699
[SPEAKER_00] pomoći

1148
00:42:07,699 --> 00:42:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] i razvoja

1149
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] dakle u zemljama

1150
00:42:10,619 --> 00:42:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] koje su primatelji pomoći

1151
00:42:12,519 --> 00:42:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] se temelja na tome

1152
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] da se mora surađivati

1153
00:42:14,820 --> 00:42:15,980
[SPEAKER_00] sa lokalnom zajednicom.

1154
00:42:15,980 --> 00:42:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] A vi se u stvari

1155
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] i prije

1156
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,639
[SPEAKER_00] nego su ove teorije

1157
00:42:19,639 --> 00:42:20,579
[SPEAKER_00] sve razrađene

1158
00:42:20,579 --> 00:42:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari to primijenili

1159
00:42:22,179 --> 00:42:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] i željeli

1160
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] sudjelovanje

1161
00:42:23,659 --> 00:42:24,780
[SPEAKER_00] lokalne zajednice

1162
00:42:24,780 --> 00:42:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] da oni pokažu

1163
00:42:25,739 --> 00:42:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] konkretno

1164
00:42:26,659 --> 00:42:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] mi,

1165
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:28,280
[SPEAKER_00] važno nam i da vi dođete

1166
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,079
[SPEAKER_00] a kasnije da vamo

1167
00:42:29,079 --> 00:42:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] u svemu drugom surađuju.

1168
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:31,340
[SPEAKER_00] Jasno.

1169
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi to uče na fakultetima

1170
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] kako se to radi

1171
00:42:35,260 --> 00:42:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] a vi ste to iz života.

1172
00:42:36,719 --> 00:42:39,139
[SPEAKER_01] To je tako jednostavno bilo

1173
00:42:39,139 --> 00:42:40,219
[SPEAKER_01] nije meni bilo trebalo

1174
00:42:40,219 --> 00:42:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] da kažem reći

1175
00:42:40,760 --> 00:42:41,719
[SPEAKER_01] sad nemate veće.

1176
00:42:42,179 --> 00:42:43,460
[SPEAKER_01] A da ja vidim kuće

1177
00:42:43,460 --> 00:42:45,320
[SPEAKER_01] šta bi ona meni pokazala.

1178
00:42:45,320 --> 00:42:45,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1179
00:42:45,579 --> 00:42:46,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kažem ja

1180
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:47,800
[SPEAKER_01] a tu je nekad bio svećenik

1181
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] je živio,

1182
00:42:48,199 --> 00:42:48,739
[SPEAKER_01] francus.

1183
00:42:48,739 --> 00:42:51,199
[SPEAKER_01] Recite mi kako se on služio svećenom.

1184
00:42:51,199 --> 00:42:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] Išao je u šumoku i drugi.

1185
00:42:52,500 --> 00:42:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kažem ja

1186
00:42:53,519 --> 00:42:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] zamislite vi sad

1187
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:55,619
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću sad tuci negdje

1188
00:42:55,619 --> 00:42:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] napraviti nekakvu malu

1189
00:42:56,940 --> 00:42:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] ogradu

1190
00:42:58,159 --> 00:42:59,360
[SPEAKER_01] od lišća, grana

1191
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] i ja ću se ići tu prat.

1192
00:43:00,679 --> 00:43:03,400
[SPEAKER_01] Da li bi to pristajalo?

1193
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:05,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite ja

1194
00:43:05,119 --> 00:43:06,179
[SPEAKER_01] nikad se ne zgida.

1195
00:43:06,179 --> 00:43:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ću ja ići sad vani?

1196
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,719
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nisam jako obična žena.

1197
00:43:09,719 --> 00:43:11,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kaže

1198
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:12,300
[SPEAKER_01] imate vi pravo

1199
00:43:12,300 --> 00:43:13,820
[SPEAKER_01] ali to nama nije palo na pamet.

1200
00:43:13,820 --> 00:43:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, pa onda ste ih podučili

1201
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:16,679
[SPEAKER_00] naši rješenje

1202
00:43:16,679 --> 00:43:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] pa su i oni vidjeli.

1203
00:43:17,780 --> 00:43:19,179
[SPEAKER_00] Da su oni to napravili

1204
00:43:19,179 --> 00:43:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] i tako to

1205
00:43:20,619 --> 00:43:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi se

1206
00:43:21,699 --> 00:43:23,280
[SPEAKER_01] vremenom se dolazi na to

1207
00:43:23,280 --> 00:43:25,400
[SPEAKER_01] ali treba puno vremena.

1208
00:43:25,400 --> 00:43:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da, treba vremena

1209
00:43:26,519 --> 00:43:27,980
[SPEAKER_00] i prisutnosti.

1210
00:43:27,980 --> 00:43:29,320
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što vi dajete

1211
00:43:29,320 --> 00:43:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] prisutnost

1212
00:43:29,940 --> 00:43:30,639
[SPEAKER_00] da ste tamo

1213
00:43:30,639 --> 00:43:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] da živite njihovu stvarnost.

1214
00:43:32,719 --> 00:43:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] Jer

1215
00:43:33,260 --> 00:43:35,980
[SPEAKER_01] može se drugačije živjeti

1216
00:43:35,980 --> 00:43:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] i to sa svim tim sredstvima

1217
00:43:37,480 --> 00:43:38,619
[SPEAKER_01] koje imate

1218
00:43:38,619 --> 00:43:39,900
[SPEAKER_01] možete drugačije

1219
00:43:39,900 --> 00:43:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] može biti bolje.

1220
00:43:40,800 --> 00:43:42,320
[SPEAKER_01] oni peru veš

1221
00:43:42,320 --> 00:43:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] operu ga

1222
00:43:43,679 --> 00:43:44,579
[SPEAKER_01] na rijeci

1223
00:43:44,579 --> 00:43:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] u kojoj se sve radi

1224
00:43:46,300 --> 00:43:47,260
[SPEAKER_01] i tu se i pije

1225
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] i pere se sve.

1226
00:43:48,179 --> 00:43:49,360
[SPEAKER_01] I sad

1227
00:43:49,360 --> 00:43:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] uzmo taj veš

1228
00:43:51,119 --> 00:43:51,900
[SPEAKER_01] i prostru

1229
00:43:51,900 --> 00:43:52,840
[SPEAKER_01] po kraj puta.

1230
00:43:53,179 --> 00:43:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] po granju stavljaju.

1231
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:57,380
[SPEAKER_00] Da, sad stavljaju i po granju.

1232
00:43:57,380 --> 00:43:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, prije nisu ni po granju.

1233
00:43:58,579 --> 00:44:00,579
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mi smo došli u selo

1234
00:44:00,579 --> 00:44:01,800
[SPEAKER_01] i kažem ja njima

1235
00:44:01,800 --> 00:44:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] da mi stave

1236
00:44:03,360 --> 00:44:04,679
[SPEAKER_01] stupove

1237
00:44:04,679 --> 00:44:05,780
[SPEAKER_01] pa ću nategnu štrik.

1238
00:44:05,780 --> 00:44:06,739
[SPEAKER_01] Stupe će staviti,

1239
00:44:06,739 --> 00:44:07,440
[SPEAKER_01] nemaju štrik.

1240
00:44:07,659 --> 00:44:08,219
[SPEAKER_01] imam ja.

1241
00:44:08,219 --> 00:44:10,280
[SPEAKER_01] I sad oni su to sve napravili

1242
00:44:10,280 --> 00:44:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] i kako se mi rekla

1243
00:44:10,940 --> 00:44:11,679
[SPEAKER_01] vidim mi sredstvom,

1244
00:44:11,679 --> 00:44:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] šta ćete vi s tim?

1245
00:44:12,599 --> 00:44:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kad operem vešek,

1246
00:44:15,420 --> 00:44:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ću ga staviti

1247
00:44:16,219 --> 00:44:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] da se suši?

1248
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:18,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tu ću ga objesiti.

1249
00:44:18,179 --> 00:44:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu ga staviti dole,

1250
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] pa biće opet prljavo.

1251
00:44:22,059 --> 00:44:23,420
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su se oni sjetili

1252
00:44:23,420 --> 00:44:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] kako oni rade.

1253
00:44:24,420 --> 00:44:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] Onda su drugi dan,

1254
00:44:26,239 --> 00:44:28,139
[SPEAKER_01] svi koji su tu bili blizu nas,

1255
00:44:28,139 --> 00:44:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] drugi dan nisu stavljali veš dole,

1256
00:44:29,880 --> 00:44:31,440
[SPEAKER_01] nego gore po granama.

1257
00:44:31,440 --> 00:44:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je taj primjerom,

1258
00:44:34,320 --> 00:44:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] životom s njima,

1259
00:44:35,659 --> 00:44:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] im se u stvari...

1260
00:44:37,199 --> 00:44:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] Na taj način

1261
00:44:38,159 --> 00:44:39,760
[SPEAKER_01] idemo naprijed.

1262
00:44:39,760 --> 00:44:40,380
[SPEAKER_01] I sad reći,

1263
00:44:40,380 --> 00:44:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] to se ne radi tako,

1264
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:42,360
[SPEAKER_01] kako ćemo?

1265
00:44:42,360 --> 00:44:43,260
[SPEAKER_01] Drugačije ne možemo

1266
00:44:43,260 --> 00:44:44,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego tako kako smo navikli.

1267
00:44:44,500 --> 00:44:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] A kad vidim da neko može drugačije,

1268
00:44:46,619 --> 00:44:47,579
[SPEAKER_01] da neko drugačije radi,

1269
00:44:47,579 --> 00:44:48,280
[SPEAKER_01] onda se to ide.

1270
00:44:48,280 --> 00:44:50,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam, Benini predivna zemlja.

1271
00:44:50,820 --> 00:44:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je lijep.

1272
00:44:52,679 --> 00:44:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, toliko je.

1273
00:44:54,199 --> 00:44:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ljudi su tako blagi,

1274
00:44:55,940 --> 00:44:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] ljubazni,

1275
00:44:57,559 --> 00:44:59,139
[SPEAKER_00] nekako baš...

1276
00:44:59,139 --> 00:44:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] Benini je poznat

1277
00:44:59,960 --> 00:45:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] po toj gostorljubivosti.

1278
00:45:02,039 --> 00:45:02,280
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1279
00:45:02,280 --> 00:45:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Jer on je jedan poseban narod

1280
00:45:04,559 --> 00:45:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] koji prijima stranca.

1281
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:08,820
[SPEAKER_01] I ono, na početku

1282
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo mi došli,

1283
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] podemo u selo

1284
00:45:11,260 --> 00:45:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] posjetiti ljude,

1285
00:45:12,539 --> 00:45:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] da vidimo malo.

1286
00:45:13,980 --> 00:45:15,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ti dođeš

1287
00:45:15,139 --> 00:45:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] kao tamo,

1288
00:45:16,460 --> 00:45:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] kod stranac,

1289
00:45:17,019 --> 00:45:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] kod njih,

1290
00:45:17,420 --> 00:45:18,420
[SPEAKER_01] oni nemaju ništa,

1291
00:45:18,420 --> 00:45:20,119
[SPEAKER_01] ono nema solicu da ti da.

1292
00:45:20,820 --> 00:45:22,239
[SPEAKER_01] on će ići negdje u selu,

1293
00:45:22,239 --> 00:45:23,320
[SPEAKER_01] netko ima stolicu,

1294
00:45:23,320 --> 00:45:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] ono će ići donijeti.

1295
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] I onda znaju,

1296
00:45:26,519 --> 00:45:27,320
[SPEAKER_01] već znaju,

1297
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] toček kod nas je tamo,

1298
00:45:29,380 --> 00:45:31,719
[SPEAKER_01] vodu vam moraju dati za popit.

1299
00:45:31,719 --> 00:45:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ne više oni znaju,

1300
00:45:33,800 --> 00:45:34,360
[SPEAKER_01] na početku,

1301
00:45:34,360 --> 00:45:35,760
[SPEAKER_01] da mi vodu ne smijemo piti.

1302
00:45:36,199 --> 00:45:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] njihovu.

1303
00:45:36,659 --> 00:45:38,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ili niste na nju navikli?

1304
00:45:38,260 --> 00:45:38,739
[SPEAKER_01] Nije,

1305
00:45:38,739 --> 00:45:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] nije voda,

1306
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] da smo upozorili,

1307
00:45:40,539 --> 00:45:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] vodu ne smijete piti.

1308
00:45:41,980 --> 00:45:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1309
00:45:42,119 --> 00:45:43,980
[SPEAKER_01] I oni to znaju,

1310
00:45:43,980 --> 00:45:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] onda će ići tražiti

1311
00:45:45,039 --> 00:45:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] negdje nekoga

1312
00:45:45,940 --> 00:45:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji ima možda

1313
00:45:46,679 --> 00:45:48,059
[SPEAKER_01] nekakav sok u flaši

1314
00:45:48,059 --> 00:45:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] zatvoren,

1315
00:45:48,579 --> 00:45:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] da donesu.

1316
00:45:49,699 --> 00:45:51,159
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kad pođete u kući,

1317
00:45:51,159 --> 00:45:51,820
[SPEAKER_01] oni vama moraju

1318
00:45:51,820 --> 00:45:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] dati nekakav poklad.

1319
00:45:52,940 --> 00:45:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] Oni moraju,

1320
00:45:54,940 --> 00:45:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] kokoš, pile,

1321
00:45:56,659 --> 00:45:57,519
[SPEAKER_01] voće,

1322
00:45:57,519 --> 00:45:58,219
[SPEAKER_01] bilo šta,

1323
00:45:58,219 --> 00:45:59,199
[SPEAKER_01] sami ne jedu,

1324
00:45:59,199 --> 00:45:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] sami nemaju,

1325
00:45:59,860 --> 00:46:00,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali moraju vama,

1326
00:46:00,519 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] stranco se mora dati

1327
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:02,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad pođe.

1328
00:46:02,480 --> 00:46:03,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vi uz ovo,

1329
00:46:03,920 --> 00:46:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

1330
00:46:04,159 --> 00:46:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] sami ste rekli,

1331
00:46:05,039 --> 00:46:05,860
[SPEAKER_00] ambulanta,

1332
00:46:05,860 --> 00:46:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] sva pomoć koju pružate njima,

1333
00:46:08,119 --> 00:46:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da se radi o zdravstvenoj pomoći,

1334
00:46:10,099 --> 00:46:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] bilo da se radi o hrani,

1335
00:46:11,260 --> 00:46:12,059
[SPEAKER_00] evo sad,

1336
00:46:12,059 --> 00:46:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu otvaranja škola,

1337
00:46:14,019 --> 00:46:16,019
[SPEAKER_00] to radite za sve,

1338
00:46:16,019 --> 00:46:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira jesu muslimani,

1339
00:46:18,260 --> 00:46:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] animisti ili katolici.

1340
00:46:19,960 --> 00:46:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kako vi svoju vjeru njima svjedočite?

1341
00:46:23,059 --> 00:46:24,039
[SPEAKER_00] Kako im je tumačite?

1342
00:46:24,039 --> 00:46:24,900
[SPEAKER_00] To mi sad...

1343
00:46:24,900 --> 00:46:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite,

1344
00:46:25,659 --> 00:46:26,719
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari,

1345
00:46:26,719 --> 00:46:28,199
[SPEAKER_01] mi njima ništa ne tumačimo.

1346
00:46:28,199 --> 00:46:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] Oni dolaziju u ambulante,

1347
00:46:29,920 --> 00:46:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] u školama radim,

1348
00:46:32,059 --> 00:46:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] dade sestre,

1349
00:46:32,880 --> 00:46:35,619
[SPEAKER_01] ali to se najviše radi preko ambulanta,

1350
00:46:35,619 --> 00:46:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] djeca.

1351
00:46:36,159 --> 00:46:39,920
[SPEAKER_01] Oni gledaju što mi radimo

1352
00:46:39,920 --> 00:46:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kako mi živimo.

1353
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:45,119
[SPEAKER_01] U se na početku znali reći nama,

1354
00:46:45,119 --> 00:46:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa kako ste mogli ostaviti

1355
00:46:47,400 --> 00:46:49,079
[SPEAKER_01] to što ste vi imali

1356
00:46:49,079 --> 00:46:51,699
[SPEAKER_01] i doći ovamo,

1357
00:46:51,699 --> 00:46:52,820
[SPEAKER_01] biti kod nas,

1358
00:46:52,820 --> 00:46:54,360
[SPEAKER_01] mi ništa ne imamo.

1359
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] I sad i nivi nemate.

1360
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] To su nam znali reći,

1361
00:46:57,219 --> 00:46:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa sad i nivi nemate.

1362
00:46:58,119 --> 00:46:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, pa,

1363
00:46:58,199 --> 00:47:00,039
[SPEAKER_00] logična pitanja.

1364
00:47:00,699 --> 00:47:01,320
[SPEAKER_01] I sad dođe,

1365
00:47:01,320 --> 00:47:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] neko vas pita,

1366
00:47:01,960 --> 00:47:03,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa zašto ste to ostavili?

1367
00:47:03,300 --> 00:47:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] Onda im kažemo.

1368
00:47:04,599 --> 00:47:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] Šta?

1369
00:47:06,119 --> 00:47:07,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ide to njima u glavu,

1370
00:47:07,860 --> 00:47:09,260
[SPEAKER_01] ali s vremenom

1371
00:47:09,260 --> 00:47:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] oni

1372
00:47:11,119 --> 00:47:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze,

1373
00:47:12,599 --> 00:47:13,780
[SPEAKER_01] počnu dolaziti,

1374
00:47:13,780 --> 00:47:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] donositi njihovu djecu na misu.

1375
00:47:17,159 --> 00:47:18,360
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su možda animisti.

1376
00:47:18,360 --> 00:47:20,039
[SPEAKER_01] A on kaže,

1377
00:47:20,039 --> 00:47:20,699
[SPEAKER_01] ja jesam.

1378
00:47:20,699 --> 00:47:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ali moj djete nije.

1379
00:47:23,460 --> 00:47:26,199
[SPEAKER_01] I ona donosi malu bebu

1380
00:47:26,199 --> 00:47:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] na misu,

1381
00:47:27,039 --> 00:47:28,760
[SPEAKER_01] djete mora slušat riječ Božju.

1382
00:47:28,760 --> 00:47:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

1383
00:47:30,760 --> 00:47:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] vidite,

1384
00:47:31,239 --> 00:47:31,860
[SPEAKER_01] to vam je to.

1385
00:47:31,860 --> 00:47:33,079
[SPEAKER_01] I sad na taj način

1386
00:47:33,079 --> 00:47:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi

1387
00:47:34,400 --> 00:47:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] mijenjaju mišljenje.

1388
00:47:36,380 --> 00:47:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] I puno,

1389
00:47:38,019 --> 00:47:40,519
[SPEAKER_01] kad jedna žena,

1390
00:47:40,679 --> 00:47:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] sin joj je imao i djeću paralizu,

1391
00:47:42,739 --> 00:47:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] sad je onako bio vazdan dole na zemlji.

1392
00:47:45,519 --> 00:47:47,119
[SPEAKER_01] I sad mi smo ga uzeli,

1393
00:47:47,119 --> 00:47:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] odneli jednu bolnicu,

1394
00:47:48,119 --> 00:47:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] da bar može sa štakama

1395
00:47:49,719 --> 00:47:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] ili u kolicima,

1396
00:47:51,340 --> 00:47:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] da ne plaziti cijelo vrijeme po zemlji.

1397
00:47:53,780 --> 00:47:55,079
[SPEAKER_01] Mama je bila s njim,

1398
00:47:55,079 --> 00:47:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] ona je bila ona prava,

1399
00:47:56,099 --> 00:47:57,760
[SPEAKER_01] prava animiskinja,

1400
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:58,380
[SPEAKER_01] imala je ona,

1401
00:47:58,380 --> 00:47:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] to je bila kao

1402
00:47:59,179 --> 00:48:01,179
[SPEAKER_01] nekakva poganska svećenica.

1403
00:48:01,179 --> 00:48:03,099
[SPEAKER_01] Nekad ni bila obučena.

1404
00:48:03,099 --> 00:48:06,059
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je ona,

1405
00:48:06,059 --> 00:48:09,059
[SPEAKER_01] i sad je ona dok je djete to bilo u bolnici,

1406
00:48:09,059 --> 00:48:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo znali par puta otić,

1407
00:48:11,199 --> 00:48:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] vidjeti ih,

1408
00:48:12,079 --> 00:48:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] nešta im donijet,

1409
00:48:13,039 --> 00:48:14,139
[SPEAKER_01] nešta im ostavit.

1410
00:48:14,139 --> 00:48:15,599
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je ona rekla,

1411
00:48:15,599 --> 00:48:16,699
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam toliko godina

1412
00:48:16,699 --> 00:48:19,320
[SPEAKER_01] u toj njihovoj grupi.

1413
00:48:19,320 --> 00:48:21,579
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam bila teško bolesna.

1414
00:48:21,579 --> 00:48:21,900
[SPEAKER_01] I djete,

1415
00:48:21,900 --> 00:48:23,300
[SPEAKER_01] nikad nitko se nije sjetio

1416
00:48:23,300 --> 00:48:24,820
[SPEAKER_01] da meni nešta pruži,

1417
00:48:24,820 --> 00:48:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] da mi pomogne.

1418
00:48:26,219 --> 00:48:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] A ovdje sam tako dugo

1419
00:48:28,619 --> 00:48:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] i nisam ne ti ono što drugi jesu.

1420
00:48:32,159 --> 00:48:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] Da nije opće vjernica,

1421
00:48:33,500 --> 00:48:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] nije katolkija,

1422
00:48:34,380 --> 00:48:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] nije povezana s vama na taj način.

1423
00:48:37,079 --> 00:48:37,679
[SPEAKER_01] I opet,

1424
00:48:38,079 --> 00:48:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] svi mi izlaze u susret

1425
00:48:39,820 --> 00:48:41,159
[SPEAKER_01] i svi mi tu gdje jesam,

1426
00:48:41,159 --> 00:48:42,679
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi mi pomažu,

1427
00:48:42,679 --> 00:48:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] iako me ne poznaju.

1428
00:48:43,940 --> 00:48:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] I sestra,

1429
00:48:45,440 --> 00:48:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] da nije bilo sestara,

1430
00:48:46,500 --> 00:48:48,179
[SPEAKER_01] još uvijek bi moje djete plazilo po.

1431
00:48:48,179 --> 00:48:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže ona,

1432
00:48:49,719 --> 00:48:51,099
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću se sad obući,

1433
00:48:51,099 --> 00:48:52,260
[SPEAKER_01] i doći u selo,

1434
00:48:52,260 --> 00:48:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] i nek svi znaju

1435
00:48:53,000 --> 00:48:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] da nisam više ono što sam bila.

1436
00:48:54,460 --> 00:48:55,500
[SPEAKER_01] A one su stvari

1437
00:48:55,500 --> 00:48:56,219
[SPEAKER_01] ne smiju obući.

1438
00:48:57,219 --> 00:48:58,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj što je obući?

1439
00:48:58,139 --> 00:48:59,239
[SPEAKER_01] Obući?

1440
00:48:59,239 --> 00:49:00,860
[SPEAKER_01] Obući gornji dio haljine.

1441
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] A, ona nikad nije nosila.

1442
00:49:02,460 --> 00:49:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, to je nesmij,

1443
00:49:03,079 --> 00:49:03,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je zabranjeno.

1444
00:49:03,940 --> 00:49:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je ona to,

1445
00:49:05,500 --> 00:49:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] nek svi znaju,

1446
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:08,480
[SPEAKER_01] ja se više njih ne bojim,

1447
00:49:08,480 --> 00:49:10,420
[SPEAKER_01] jer to nije ništa što smo mi imali dosad.

1448
00:49:10,960 --> 00:49:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] To je na taj način,

1449
00:49:12,619 --> 00:49:13,539
[SPEAKER_01] taj rad

1450
00:49:13,539 --> 00:49:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] i to svjedočanstvo,

1451
00:49:15,679 --> 00:49:17,139
[SPEAKER_01] puno priča ne vrijedi.

1452
00:49:17,139 --> 00:49:18,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tek posle,

1453
00:49:18,280 --> 00:49:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] kad oni počnu se zanimat,

1454
00:49:19,840 --> 00:49:21,179
[SPEAKER_01] postavljati pitanja,

1455
00:49:21,179 --> 00:49:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] onda ih možete objašnjavati

1456
00:49:23,019 --> 00:49:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] ono što ih zanima

1457
00:49:23,880 --> 00:49:25,300
[SPEAKER_01] i reći im istinu.

1458
00:49:25,300 --> 00:49:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] A ovako ići u prazno,

1459
00:49:27,519 --> 00:49:28,519
[SPEAKER_00] ne smisla.

1460
00:49:28,519 --> 00:49:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] Krenuli smo razgovor

1461
00:49:31,460 --> 00:49:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] s Marinim obrocima.

1462
00:49:32,440 --> 00:49:35,099
[SPEAKER_00] Evo sad da na neki način završimo.

1463
00:49:35,099 --> 00:49:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] Za Marine obroke također

1464
00:49:36,980 --> 00:49:38,599
[SPEAKER_00] mora u,

1465
00:49:38,599 --> 00:49:40,659
[SPEAKER_00] kada se otvori kuhinja,

1466
00:49:40,739 --> 00:49:41,619
[SPEAKER_00] mora sudjelovati

1467
00:49:41,619 --> 00:49:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] i lokalna zajednica.

1468
00:49:43,099 --> 00:49:44,900
[SPEAKER_00] Oni donose drva?

1469
00:49:44,900 --> 00:49:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] Donose drva,

1470
00:49:45,880 --> 00:49:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] vodu.

1471
00:49:47,400 --> 00:49:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] Njihova je na njihovom redima voda

1472
00:49:50,460 --> 00:49:51,579
[SPEAKER_01] i drva.

1473
00:49:51,579 --> 00:49:53,820
[SPEAKER_01] I recimo žene koji kuhaju,

1474
00:49:53,820 --> 00:49:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] nemoguće je kod nac

1475
00:49:55,980 --> 00:49:56,820
[SPEAKER_01] biti volonter.

1476
00:49:56,820 --> 00:49:58,380
[SPEAKER_01] Potpuno.

1477
00:49:58,380 --> 00:50:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svaka ta žena

1478
00:50:00,500 --> 00:50:01,679
[SPEAKER_01] mora ići u polje

1479
00:50:01,679 --> 00:50:02,400
[SPEAKER_01] ili na trežnicu

1480
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] da bi nešto

1481
00:50:02,980 --> 00:50:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] privredila za ubitelj.

1482
00:50:05,019 --> 00:50:05,619
[SPEAKER_01] I onda

1483
00:50:05,619 --> 00:50:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] tima ženama se treba dati nešto

1484
00:50:07,940 --> 00:50:09,159
[SPEAKER_01] po danu,

1485
00:50:09,159 --> 00:50:09,880
[SPEAKER_01] tjednom,

1486
00:50:09,880 --> 00:50:10,659
[SPEAKER_01] mjesečno.

1487
00:50:10,659 --> 00:50:12,699
[SPEAKER_01] a to je na njihovoj

1488
00:50:12,699 --> 00:50:15,179
[SPEAKER_01] volji

1489
00:50:15,179 --> 00:50:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] kako će one osigurati

1490
00:50:17,119 --> 00:50:17,820
[SPEAKER_00] te žene.

1491
00:50:17,820 --> 00:50:19,139
[SPEAKER_00] Kako će te žene

1492
00:50:19,139 --> 00:50:21,280
[SPEAKER_00] među sobom se organizirati

1493
00:50:21,280 --> 00:50:21,719
[SPEAKER_00] da dolaze.

1494
00:50:21,719 --> 00:50:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ali vi ste,

1495
00:50:22,519 --> 00:50:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] meni je toliko bilo lijepo,

1496
00:50:23,900 --> 00:50:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] vi tu djecu,

1497
00:50:24,500 --> 00:50:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] vi imate raspored da

1498
00:50:25,920 --> 00:50:27,219
[SPEAKER_00] djeca znaju

1499
00:50:27,219 --> 00:50:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad trebaju donijeti drva.

1500
00:50:28,340 --> 00:50:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda djete dolaze u školu,

1501
00:50:29,619 --> 00:50:30,940
[SPEAKER_00] nosi nekoliko komada drva

1502
00:50:30,940 --> 00:50:31,980
[SPEAKER_00] za kuhanje ručka.

1503
00:50:32,119 --> 00:50:34,199
[SPEAKER_01] to djeca donose i to na pomažu,

1504
00:50:34,199 --> 00:50:34,579
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

1505
00:50:34,579 --> 00:50:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] učitelji,

1506
00:50:35,059 --> 00:50:36,079
[SPEAKER_01] direktori škole.

1507
00:50:36,639 --> 00:50:38,460
[SPEAKER_01] to je njihovo i oni znaju kad djeca

1508
00:50:38,460 --> 00:50:39,679
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ima drva,

1509
00:50:39,679 --> 00:50:41,199
[SPEAKER_01] koliko treba donijet kad,

1510
00:50:41,199 --> 00:50:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] a rijetko kad drva fale,

1511
00:50:42,860 --> 00:50:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] mi moramo kupiti,

1512
00:50:43,920 --> 00:50:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] onda dodati nešto.

1513
00:50:45,079 --> 00:50:48,679
[SPEAKER_01] Ali redovito su to manje količine za drva,

1514
00:50:48,679 --> 00:50:50,679
[SPEAKER_01] jer donose djeca,

1515
00:50:50,679 --> 00:50:51,539
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji.

1516
00:50:52,099 --> 00:50:53,699
[SPEAKER_01] Tako smo krenuli od početka

1517
00:50:53,699 --> 00:50:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] i tako idemo dalje.

1518
00:50:55,300 --> 00:50:57,679
[SPEAKER_01] Sad otvaramo petu školu,

1519
00:50:57,679 --> 00:51:00,139
[SPEAKER_01] početkom u devetom mjesecu,

1520
00:51:00,139 --> 00:51:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad posne škola,

1521
00:51:01,039 --> 00:51:03,280
[SPEAKER_01] oni će imati hranu,

1522
00:51:03,280 --> 00:51:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] oni osiguravaju vodu

1523
00:51:05,260 --> 00:51:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] i koliko bude trebalo još,

1524
00:51:08,320 --> 00:51:09,480
[SPEAKER_01] možda nešto pjeska,

1525
00:51:09,480 --> 00:51:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] malo radne snage.

1526
00:51:10,599 --> 00:51:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] I onda su rekli,

1527
00:51:11,860 --> 00:51:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] učitelji tu će aktivirati čak i djecu.

1528
00:51:14,659 --> 00:51:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] Uključiti da svi,

1529
00:51:16,420 --> 00:51:18,239
[SPEAKER_00] da je to njihova kutinja,

1530
00:51:18,239 --> 00:51:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] da je to njihovo i da su oni doprinjeli svojim radom.

1531
00:51:21,980 --> 00:51:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, evo sjeca,

1532
00:51:23,159 --> 00:51:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] puno vam hvala za ove razgovore,

1533
00:51:25,380 --> 00:51:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] opet nekako sam doznala nove stvari.

1534
00:51:28,780 --> 00:51:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vama i hvala svim onima

1535
00:51:30,840 --> 00:51:33,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji nam pomažu da možemo tamo raditi

1536
00:51:33,679 --> 00:51:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] i nahraniti tu djecu.

1537
00:51:35,739 --> 00:51:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nema ovih odavdje koji daju nešto malo,

1538
00:51:39,519 --> 00:51:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] tebiško bi mi to...

1539
00:51:40,739 --> 00:51:43,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro, bez vas se tamo ništa ne bi moglo raditi.

1540
00:51:43,599 --> 00:51:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, treba i jedno i drugo.

1541
00:51:44,760 --> 00:51:46,059
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo si pružiti ruke,

1542
00:51:46,059 --> 00:51:47,360
[SPEAKER_01] makar bile kako daleko,

1543
00:51:47,360 --> 00:51:49,820
[SPEAKER_01] ipak se možemo dodirnuti po nekim dobrim dijelima

1544
00:51:49,820 --> 00:51:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] i onda tako povezujemo se

1545
00:51:51,860 --> 00:51:52,980
[SPEAKER_01] to je imao sve nekako jače,

1546
00:51:52,980 --> 00:51:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim o tome i na taj način.

1547
00:51:56,940 --> 00:51:58,400
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, hvala puno.

1548
00:51:58,400 --> 00:52:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] Vele gledatelji, hvala da ste nas pratili.

1549
00:52:00,920 --> 00:52:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pozdravljam vas do sljedećeg videa.

1550
00:52:30,920 --> 00:53:00,900
[UNKNOWN] Hvala što pratite kanal.

